h%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOver%20100%20people%20wrote%20in%20about%20why%20they%20shop%20there%20(hint%3A%20its%20the%20prices).%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20holiday%20season%2C%20I%20bought%20a%20bunch%20of%20gift%20items%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-temu-chinese-app-amazon-safe-legit-pinduoduo-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETemu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Chinese%20ecommerce%20app%20that%20has%20exploded%20in%20the%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3Ea%20set%20of%20minature%20pots%2C%20pans%2C%20and%20cooking%20utensils%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3Estickers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3Ea%20fanny%20pack%20that%20looks%20like%20a%20gel%20silica%20pack%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3Epencil%20sharpeners%20that%20look%20like%20noses%20where%20you%20stick%20the%20pencil%20up%20the%20nostril%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3Ean%20unlicensed%20Elsa%20princess%20costume%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3Ea%20baseball%20hat%20that%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bwomen%20want%20me%2C%20fish%20fear%20me%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3Ea%20pizza%20cutter%20wheel%20that%20looks%20like%20an%20axe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20these%20items%20were%20under%20%2410%2C%20most%20of%20them%20around%20%242%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20were%20absolute%20hits%20as%20gifts.%20I%20assumed%20that%20many%20people%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftemu-passes-shein-in-traffic-purchasing-visits-hasnt-surpassed-amazon-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshopped%20on%20Temu%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20way%20I%20did%3A%20looking%20for%20weird%2C%20surprising%2C%20cheap%20delights%20that%20I%20never%20even%20knew%20existed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20surprised%20when%20I%20read%20a%20research%20study%20recently%20that%20said%20that%20Gen%20X%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomers-not-enough-retirement-savings-gen-z-millennials-eldercare-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboomer%3C%2Fa%3E%20Temu%20shoppers%20tended%20to%20spend%20slightly%20more%20per%20order%20and%20placed%20orders%20more%20often%20than%20younger%20shoppers.%20My%20assumption%20was%20that%20Temu%20was%20targeted%20more%20at%20millennial%20and%20Gen%20Z%20shoppers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20asked%20readers%20who%20were%20boomers%20or%20Gen%20Xers%20to%20write%20in%20and%20tell%20me%3A%20Why%20do%20they%20love%20Temu%20so%20much%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20125%20people%20sent%20me%20emails%20professing%20their%20love%20(ok%2C%20well%2C%20sometimes%20reluctant%20appreciation).%20Over%20and%20over%2C%20people%20gave%20the%20same%20reason%3A%20the%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20theme%20emerged%2C%20as%20well%3A%20that%20people%20were%20using%20Temu%20for%20purchases%20they%20would%20previously%20buy%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Famazon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20surprised%20me.%20I%20would%20have%20guessed%20different%20behaviors%20for%20Amazon%20(searching%20for%20specific%20items%20you%20need)%20vs.%20Temu%20(browsing%20for%20delights).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20some%20said%20they%20liked%20it%20because%20of%20that%20browsing%20whimsy%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Ehere's%20a%20gimzo%20you%20never%20knew%20existed!%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eelement.%20In%20semi-recent%20history%2C%20these%20were%20the%20things%20you'd%20find%20wandering%20through%20Bed%2C%20Bath%20%26amp%3B%20Beyond%20(now%20out%20of%20business)%20or%20late-night%20TV%20infomercials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20study%20suggested%20that%20some%20of%20Temu's%20appeal%20to%20older%20shoppers%20was%20its%20gamified%20spinny%20wheels%2C%20which%20might%20trick%20less%20digitally%20savvy%20people.%20The%20Gen%20X%20and%20boomers%20denied%20this%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0most%20of%20them%20said%20they%20ignored%20the%20annoying%20roulette%20wheels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20what%20a%20few%20Gen%20Xers%20and%20boomers%20told%20me%2C%20starting%20with%20a%20shopper%20who%20said%20Temu%20triggers%20nostalgia%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EMy%20father%20used%20to%20have%20a%20kitchen%20drawer%20full%20of%20knickknacks%20or%20some%20junk%20he'd%20find%20from%20a%20TV%20commercial%20(As%20Seen%20On%20TV%20commercials).%20Temu%20brings%20back%20that%20nostalgia%20for%20me%20plus%20I%20find%20items%20that%20genuinely%20makes%20life%20a%20little%20easier.%20A%20lot%20of%20it%20comes%20in%20handy.%20Most%20of%20the%20times%2C%20they%20have%20something%20that%20you%20never%20knew%20that%20you%20needed%2C%20like%20bag%20sealers%20and%20small%20motion%20activated%20lights.%20%E2%80%94%3Cem%3ETyrone%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20boomer%20with%20a%20Temu%20%26quot%3Baddiction%3A%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20life%20I%20have%20an%20addiction.%20I%20cannot%20for%20the%20life%20of%20me%20explain%20why%20I%20have%20a%20need%20to%20order%20from%20Temu.%C2%A0Yes%2C%20I'm%20a%20boomer.%20Yes%2C%20I%20have%20a%20big%20house%20that%20I%20am%20never%20moving%20out%20of.%2035%20yrs%20ago%20we%20filled%20it%20with%20antiques.%20Then%20came%20babies%20and%20it%20was%20filled%20with%20toys%20etc.%20They're%20gone%20%26amp%3B%20then%20came%20the%20dog%20with%20all%20the%20dog%20toys%2C%20beds%2C%20bowls%2C%20crates%20etc.%20Dog%20is%20gone%20after%2015%20years%20and%20now%20I%20see%20things%20I%20think%20I%20need%20on%20Temu.%20It%20started%20with%20seeing%20little%20toys%20to%20fill%20the%20grandkid's%20Christmas%20stockings.%20Now%20it's%20just%20out%20of%20control.%20%E2%80%94%3Cem%3ELinda%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20kindergarten%20teacher%20who%20doesn't%20mind%20the%20quality%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EI%20am%20a%2058%20year%20old%20woman%20from%20the%20Toronto%20area%20who%20loves%20Temu.%20Yes%20I%20know%20the%20products%20are%20mostly%20made%20of%20inferior%20materials%20and%20are%20from%20China%2C%20but%20I%20find%20the%20costumes%20jewelry%2C%20home%20decor%20and%20gifts%20for%20my%20kindergarten%20students%20and%20teenage%20kids%20are%20priceless%20(ha%20ha%20pun%20intended!)%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20have%20purchased%20probably%20about%20%24300%20of%20stuff%20over%20the%20past%20year%20and%20I%20have%20only%20been%20disappointed%20with%20one%20product%3A%20a%20cute%20little%20cat%20ring%20that%20I%20bought%20for%20my%20son.%20It%20wasn't%20even%20close%20to%20being%20as%20cute%20as%20advertised%2C%20but%20for%20%243.50%2C%20what%20do%20you%20want%3F%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94Lanie%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224096%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20variety%20of%20items%20bought%20on%20temu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd46bf6fcb546d2d4bc060%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224096%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20variety%20of%20items%20bought%20by%20a%20Gen%20Xer%20on%20Temu%3Cp%3EKristy%20Meeks%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20crafter%20who%20gets%20jewelry-making%20supplies%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EI%20shop%20on%20Temu%20mostly%20for%20jewelry%2C%20crafting%20and%20jewelry%20supplies.%20I%20can%20buy%20them%20on%20Temu%20for%20less%20than%20half%20of%20what%20it%20would%20cost%20me%20to%20buy%20the%20exact%20same%20thing%20on%20Amazon%20or%20Etsy.%20My%20latest%20obsession%20is%20the%20Pandora%20style%20bracelet%20charms.%20I%20have%20a%20bracelet%20full%20of%20charms%2C%20the%20most%20expensive%20one%20was%20%2413.%20It%20would%20have%20cost%20a%20couple%20hundred%20dollars%20if%20I%20would%20have%20bought%20them%20on%20Amazon%20or%20directly%20from%20the%20manufacturer.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94Lydia%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Chr%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20DIY%20home%20improvement%20shopper%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20majority%20of%20my%20purchases%20have%20been%20camping%20or%20home%20improvement%20items.%20No%20tchotchkes!%20A%20random%20sampling%20of%20what%20I've%20purchased%20are%3A%20solar%2Fhandcrank%20emergency%20radio%2C%20pop-up%20privacy%20shelter%2C%20solar%20water%20heater%2C%20emergency%20foil%20blankets%2C%20fold%20up%20cookstove%2C%20privacy%20window%20film%2C%20brass%20winterizing%20valve%20set%2C%20garden%20netting%2C%20microwave%20splatter%20shield%2C%20and%20houseplant%20watering%20system.%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%94Randy%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20engraving%20hobbyist%20who%20gets%20his%20tools%20from%20Temu%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EWe%20moved%20into%20a%20new%20flat%20and%20discovered%20Temu%20while%20shopping%20for%20stuff%20we%20needed%20to%20adapt%20the%20new%20place%3A%20light%20fixtures%2C%20ceiling%20fans%2C%20wall%20holders%20for%20soap%2Fshampoo%2Fsponges%2C%20light%20fixture%20for%20multi-ceiling%20light%20to%20better%20fit%20dining%2Fliving%20room%20space%2C%20other%20utilitarian%20stuff%20for%20kitchen%20%E2%80%A6%20Here's%20Temu%20stuff%20for%20home%20craft%20work%2C%20including%20tools%20%26amp%3B%20protective%20mat%20for%20engraving%2Flithography%2C%20special%20tape%20for%20collages%2C%20stamp%20press%20tool%2C%20mini%20paint%20rollers...%20(plus%20an%20unrelated%204-way%20light%20cable%20splitter).%20Cost%20maybe%20%2415%20in%20all%3F%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20Bill%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22craft%20supplies%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b969f443bb77284ba1e71f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECraft%20supples%2C%20about%20%2415%20total.%3Cp%3EBill%20Eldridge%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20boomer%20who%20doesn't%20mind%20off-brand%20items%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EAs%20Boomers%20we%20don't%20place%20so%20much%20emphasis%20on%20wearing%20name%20brand%20clothing%20and%20accessories.%C2%A0%20Our%20focus%20is%20on%20saving%20money%20to%20enjoy%20other%20activities%20and%20pay%20our%20bills.%20Also%2C%20the%20convenience%20of%20shopping%20online.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EHelen%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-gen-x-boomers-love-temu-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707049142000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd57597a3d2714887753bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-gen-x-boomers-love-temu-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20100%20people%20wrote%20emails%20to%20me%20about%20why%20they%20love%20Temu.%20One%20boomer%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20place%20so%20much%20emphasis%20on%20wearing%20name-brand%20clothing.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-gen-x-boomers-love-temu-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22He%20called%20himself%20the%20Timepiece%20Gentlemen.%20Now%20he's%20facing%20hard%20time.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farrer%20walking%20away%20on%20a%20watch%20with%20his%20shadow%20as%20a%20burglar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65942c761c5c7b8c9a0d38ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnthony%20Farrer%2C%20aka%20the%20Timepiece%20Gentleman%2C%20became%20famous%20for%20selling%20luxury%20watches.%20Then%20the%20Feds%20caught%20up%20with%20him.%3Cp%3ERichard%20Chance%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20after%20dark%2C%20the%20most%20wanted%20man%20on%20Reddit%20slipped%20into%20his%20secret%20lair%3A%20a%20storage%20locker%20behind%20a%20Gold's%20Gym%20in%20Venice%2C%20California.%20%26quot%3BI've%20got%20another%20storage%20unit%20full%20of%20merch%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthony%20Farrer%20told%20me%20as%20I%20followed%20him%20inside.%20%26quot%3BI%20still%20have%20a%20ton%20of%20followers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarrer%20is%20better%20known%20as%20the%20Timepiece%20Gentleman%2C%20the%20flashiest%20online%20dealer%20in%20the%20%2475%20billion%20luxury%20watch%20trade.%20Chiseled%20and%20steely%20like%20his%20hero%20Mark%20Wahlberg%2C%20whom%20he%20resembles%20enough%20to%20have%20earned%20the%20nickname%20Marky%20Mark%20in%20high%20school%2C%20the%2035-year-old%20Texan%20was%20wearing%20long%20black%20shorts%2C%20a%20tight%20black%20T-shirt%2C%20and%20a%20snappy%20black%20TPG%20cap%20on%20his%20closely%20shorn%20head.%20During%20the%20COVID%20timepiece%20boom%2C%20when%20guys%20rich%20on%20crypto%20and%20locked%20down%20during%20the%20pandemic%20were%20blowing%20millions%20on%20six-figure%20Rolexes%20and%20Patek%20Philippes%2C%20Farrer%20became%20internet%20famous%20for%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKx7wZUiRHp8%26t%3D100s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eflex%20videos%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20private%20jets%2C%20sushi%20feasts%2C%20and%20doing%20doughnuts%20in%20his%20%24170%2C000%20cherry-red%20Audi%20R8%20in%20an%20Office%20Depot%20parking%20lot%20(until%20a%20weary%20security%20guard%20asked%20him%20to%20leave).%20Amassing%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20fans%20on%20Instagram%20and%20YouTube%2C%20he%20opened%20up%20the%20notoriously%20shady%20world%20of%20watch%20sales%2C%20showing%20viewers%20how%20he%20evaluated%20watches%2C%20made%20deals%2C%20and%20busted%20counterfeit%20sellers.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20something%20people%20had%20never%20seen%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Roman%20Sharf%2C%20a%20veteran%20watch%20dealer.%20%26quot%3BHe%20literally%20lifted%20up%20the%20curtain%20of%20this%20multibillion-dollar%20industry%20that%20has%20never%20been%20shown%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20inside%20his%20storage%20locker%2C%20Farrer%20showed%20me%20his%20inventory%20of%20Timepiece%20Gentleman%20swag%3A%20branded%20hoodies%20(%26quot%3Bmade%20in%20the%20same%20factory%20as%20Balenciaga%20and%20Prada%26quot%3B)%2C%20custom%20leather%20wristwatch%20attaches%20(%26quot%3Bhigh-quality%20%241%2C200%20briefcases%26quot%3B)%2C%20and%20signature%20black%20marble%20watch%20stands%20(%26quot%3Bfor%20when%20you're%20sitting%20at%20your%20desk%20and%20don't%20want%20to%20get%20scratches%20all%20over%20your%20watch%26quot%3B).%20But%20stacked%20neatly%20on%20a%20far%20shelf%20were%20tokens%20of%20his%20current%2C%20considerably%20less%20glamorous%20reality%3A%20cans%20of%20tuna%20fish%2C%20bars%20of%20soap%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20pillows%2C%20and%20a%20sleeping%20bag.%20The%20man%20who%20once%20made%20headlines%20for%20renting%20LA's%20most%20expensive%20apartment%20%E2%80%94%20a%20downtown%20penthouse%20he%20rented%20for%20%2490%2C000%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%20was%20now%20homeless.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20afford%20to%20keep%20spending%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20just%20sleep%20on%20the%20beach.%26quot%3B%20For%20the%20past%20two%20weeks%20he'd%20been%20living%20off%20his%20stash%20of%20canned%20food%2C%20showering%20at%20Gold's%2C%20and%20crashing%20in%20a%20lifeguard%20stand%20on%20Venice%20Beach.%20%26quot%3BI%20haven't%20had%20sushi%20for%20three%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20lamented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarrer%20was%20on%20the%20run.%20According%20to%20the%20FBI%2C%20the%20Timepiece%20Gentlemen%20financed%20his%20lavish%20lifestyle%20by%20running%20a%20%26quot%3Bluxury%20watch%20Ponzi-type%20scheme.%26quot%3B%20Using%20the%20internet%2C%20the%20authorities%20said%2C%20Farrer%20had%20conned%20his%20wealthy%20buyers%20out%20of%20millions%2C%20taking%20their%20watches%20to%20sell%20on%20consignment%20and%20then%20using%20the%20proceeds%20to%20buy%20more%20watches%2C%20all%20in%20a%20desperate%20race%20to%20keep%20ahead%20of%20his%20creditors.%20A%20foster%20kid%20from%20backwoods%20Texas%2C%20Farrer%20had%20broken%20into%20the%20rarefied%20world%20of%20luxury%20timepieces%2C%20defying%20its%20unwritten%20rules%20and%20exposing%20its%20sleaziest%20secrets.%20But%20in%20the%20process%2C%20he%20had%20relied%20on%20techniques%20that%20were%20dubious%20at%20best%20and%20criminal%20at%20worst.%20Small%20wonder%20that%20the%20sleuths%20on%20Reddit%2C%20who%20had%20been%20working%20for%20years%20to%20bring%20him%20down%2C%20had%20given%20him%20a%20nickname%20befitting%20a%20scam%20artist%3A%20the%20Wolf%20of%20Watch%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20think%20I'm%20such%20a%20monster%2C%26quot%3B%20Farrer%20told%20me%20as%20he%20lowered%20the%20door%20of%20his%20storage%20unit%20and%20secured%20it%20with%20a%20lock.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20don't%20want%20one%20little%20failure%20to%20erase%20everything%20I've%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20FBI%20agents%20stormed%20the%20locker%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-cdca%2Fpr%2Ffounder-beverly-hills-gentlemen-timepieces-consignment-store-charged-conning-victims%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Earrested%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Farrer%20on%2011%20counts%20of%20wire%20and%20mail%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EFarrer%20got%20his%20first%20watch%20around%20the%20time%20he%20pulled%20two%20butcher%20knives%20on%20his%20dad.%20It%20was%202005%20and%20Farrer%2C%2017%2C%20was%20living%20with%20his%20foster%20parents%20in%20the%20cowpoke%20town%20of%20Sherman%2C%20Texas.%20The%20watch%2C%20which%20he%20bought%20with%20%24120%20from%20his%20paycheck%20at%20Buffalo%20Wild%20Wings%2C%20was%20a%20Fossil%2C%20with%20a%20dial%20that%20blinked%20blue%20and%20green.%20The%20knives%2C%20one%20in%20each%20hand%2C%20were%20of%20unknown%20provenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%20report%2C%20Farrer%20insisted%20he'd%20pulled%20the%20knives%20in%20self-defense%20after%20his%20father%20hit%20him%20in%20the%20face%20for%20not%20fixing%20a%20fence.%20It%20was%2C%20he%20told%20me%2C%20a%20reaction%20to%20years%20of%20recriminations%20and%20restrictions%20from%20his%20dad.%20%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20me%20being%20afraid%20of%20him%2C%20I%20wanted%20him%20to%20be%20afraid%20of%20me%20for%20once%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20actually%20ever%20going%20to%20stab%20somebody.%26quot%3B%20His%20parents%20told%20the%20police%20their%20son%20had%20shoved%20his%20dad%20first%20and%20threatened%20to%20kill%20him.%20Farrer%20was%20charged%20with%20aggravated%20assault%20with%20a%20deadly%20weapon%2C%20resulting%20in%20another%20of%20his%20many%20stints%20behind%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20his%20own%20account%2C%20Farrer%20was%20an%20angry%20kid.%20Angry%20his%20parents%20were%20too%20strict.%20Angry%20he%20couldn't%20be%20like%20the%20popular%20teens%20he%20saw%20on%20TV.%20Angry%20for%20reasons%20he%20couldn't%20explain.%20At%20first%2C%20he%20poured%20his%20fury%20into%20the%20gym%2C%20getting%20hooked%20on%20working%20out.%20Then%20his%20twin%20brother%2C%20Cameron%2C%20died%20in%20a%20motorcycle%20crash%2C%20and%20something%20inside%20him%20snapped.%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20bury%20that%20trauma%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled.%20%26quot%3BI%20went%20off%20the%20deep%20end.%26quot%3B%20For%20years%20he%20was%20in%20and%20out%20of%20jail%20for%20DUIs%2C%20drunken%20brawls%2C%20and%20high-speed%20chases%20with%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20through%20it%20all%2C%20he%20always%20came%20home%20to%20his%20watches.%20Collecting%20them%20had%20become%20an%20obsession.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20them%20for%20every%20different%20outfit%2C%20every%20different%20occasion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%20It%20was%20an%20expensive%20hobby%20for%20a%20poor%20kid%20from%20the%20sticks.%20So%20he%20paid%20for%20them%20with%20one%20of%20the%20few%20employment%20options%20he%20could%20find%20as%20a%20young%20ex-con.%20While%20working%20as%20a%20dancer%20in%20a%20gay%20bar%20in%20Dallas%2C%20Farrer%20gave%20%26quot%3Berotic%20massages%26quot%3B%20to%20clients%20under%20the%20alias%20Travis%20Baker.%20Before%20long%2C%20he%20wasn't%20just%20wearing%20pricey%20watches%20on%20his%20hard-working%20wrists%20%E2%80%94%20he%20discovered%20they%20could%20provide%20him%20with%20a%20lucrative%20side%20hustle.%20Flipping%20a%20single%20Breitling%20Superocean%20Heritage%20chronograph%20earned%20him%20%241%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20several%20happy%20endings%20combined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222656%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farrer%20s%20an%20exotic%20dancer%20in%20a%20club%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65942df0ec62ab5daf7fed12%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222921%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20his%20twin's%20death%2C%20Farrer%20funded%20his%20watch%20obsession%20by%20working%20as%20a%20dancer%20in%20a%20gay%20bar.%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20bury%20that%20trauma.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ERichard%20Chance%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Farrer%20was%20freshly%20out%20of%20prison%20after%20another%20DUI.%20He'd%20missed%20the%20death%20of%20his%20mother%20and%20the%20birth%20of%20his%20son.%20Dead%20broke%20and%20saddled%20with%20an%20ankle%20monitor%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20reinvent%20himself%20in%20the%20one%20place%20where%20you%20could%20create%20an%20entirely%20new%20identity%2C%20free%20of%20charge%3A%20the%20internet.%20All%20he%20needed%20was%20the%20right%20name%20for%20his%20luxury%20watch%20business%20%E2%80%94%20something%20distinctive%2C%20something%20memorable.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20one%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20imagined%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20build%20this%20account%20up%20to%20the%20point%20where%20someone's%20going%20to%20walk%20up%20and%20call%20me%20by%20my%20Instagram%20handle.%26quot%3B%20In%20his%20mind%2C%20he%20pictured%20what%20the%20ultimate%20luxury%20watch%20dealer%20would%20look%20like.%20%26quot%3BAn%20eligible%20bachelor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20thought.%20%26quot%3BA%20wealthy%20guy%20in%20his%20penthouse%20apartment%20somewhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20with%20that%2C%20Anthony%20Farrer%20transformed%20himself%20into%20the%20Timepiece%20Gentleman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gray%20market%20for%20luxury%20watches%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20from%20sleazy%20dudes%20hawking%20Rolexes%20in%20Times%20Square.%20Inspired%20by%20the%20flashy%20collectors%20they%20see%20on%20social%20media%2C%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20aficionados%20is%20spending%20billions%20on%20watches%20as%20alternative%20investments%20that%20outperform%20the%20S%26amp%3BP.%20According%20to%20a%20recent%20report%20by%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group%2C%20the%20average%20price%20of%20high-end%20timepieces%20grew%20by%2020%25%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20And%20today%2C%20nearly%20one-third%20of%20all%20luxury%20watch%20purchases%2C%20an%20estimated%20%2422%20billion%20worth%2C%20are%20pre-owned.%20While%20the%20secondhand%20trade%20isn't%20illegal%2C%20it%20is%20unregulated%2C%20which%20means%20anyone%20with%20an%20Instagram%20account%20and%20some%20fancy%20watch%20shots%20can%20start%20slinging%20jewelry.%20And%20that%20sounded%20like%20a%20hell%20of%20an%20opportunity%20to%20Anthony%20Farrer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20launch%20his%20career%20as%20the%20Timepiece%20Gentleman%2C%20Farrer%20boned%20up%20on%20the%20jargon%20of%20horology%2C%20from%20escape%20wheels%20and%20spring%20barrels%20to%20flinques%20and%20guilloches.%20It's%20a%20time-honored%20part%20of%20watch%20sales%3A%20Buyers%20love%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20feel%20they're%20being%20initiated%20into%20a%20world%20with%20its%20own%20specialized%20language%2C%20the%20mark%20of%20a%20true%20connoisseur.%20Farrer%20also%20studied%20online%20courses%20on%20the%20watch%20business%20and%20social-media%20marketing%2C%20immersing%20himself%20in%20sales%20techniques.%20Then%2C%20each%20night%2C%20he%20would%20grab%20a%20black%20backpack%20stuffed%20full%20of%20watches%20and%20head%20to%20the%20bar%20of%20a%20steakhouse%20in%20Dallas.%20But%20he%20wasn't%20going%20to%20drink%20%E2%80%94%20he%20was%20still%20on%20probation%2C%20and%20staying%20sober.%20He%20was%20going%20to%20hustle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20started%20with%20the%20buyers.%20The%20luxury%20watch%20crowd%20isn't%20just%20big-name%20celebrities%20like%20Mark%20Wahlberg%20and%20Kevin%20Hart.%20It's%20guys%20who%20made%20their%20money%20as%20roofers%2C%20as%20plumbers%20%E2%80%94%20people%2C%20Farrer%20realized%2C%20who%20%26quot%3Bcame%20from%20nothing%2C%26quot%3B%20just%20as%20he%20did.%20He%20gauged%20his%20targets%20by%20their%20drinks%20and%20their%20timepieces%20%E2%80%94%20approaching%20only%20those%20swilling%20top-shelf%20booze%20and%20sporting%20high-end%20watches.%20Then%20he'd%20move%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20position%20myself%20to%20the%20right-hand%20side%20of%20them%2C%20so%20they%20could%20see%20my%20watch%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20my%20goal.%20Every%20time%20I%20reach%20for%20my%20water%2C%20my%20watch%20is%20constantly%20in%20their%20way.%20And%20I%20would%20just%20wait.%20I%20would%20always%20let%20them%20initiate.%20And%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20initiate%20a%20conversation%2C%20then%20I%20open%20up%20for%20dialogue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20his%20YouTube-schooled%20schmoozing%20techniques%2C%20Farrer%20told%20a%20good%20tale%20to%20the%20Texans%20at%20the%20bar%3A%20small-town%20kid%20in%20the%20big%20city%2C%20flipping%20his%20only%20watch%20after%20prison%20for%20a%20thousand%20bucks%2C%20now%20dealing%20to%20other%20good%20old%20boys%20like%20himself%20as%20a%20way%20to%20redeem%20himself%20from%20his%20criminal%20past.%20It%20didn't%20matter%20that%20he%20didn't%20have%20a%20retail%20store%2C%20let%20alone%20any%20inventory.%20He%20had%20the%20internet.%20Using%20photos%20of%20other%20people's%20stock%2C%20he%20flooded%20Craigslist%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fanthony%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EInstagram%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20timepieces%20he%20passed%20off%20as%20his%20own.%20He%20also%20broke%20a%20taboo%20of%20the%20secondary%20watch%20trade%2C%20which%20thrived%20on%20markups%2C%20by%20posting%20the%20actual%20retail%20price%20of%20each%20watch.%20Buyers%20liked%20the%20transparency.%20Before%20long%2C%20he%20had%20more%20than%2035%2C000%20followers.%20%26quot%3BFor%20a%20watch%20account%2C%20that%20was%20the%20equivalent%20of%20some%20hot%20chick%20having%203%20million%20followers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20boasts.%20%26quot%3BExcept%20I%20made%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20jack%20his%20profile%20even%20higher%2C%20Farrer%20hired%20a%20videographer%2C%20Darby%20McVay%2C%20to%20follow%20him%20around%20and%20create%20a%20Timepiece%20Gentleman%20series%20on%20YouTube.%20Despite%20the%20staggering%20size%20of%20the%20luxury%20watch%20trade%2C%20nobody%20had%20thought%20to%20market%20its%20glamour%20and%20mystique.%20Farrer%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20trade%20on%20his%20tale%20of%20personal%20recovery%2C%20take%20buyers%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20and%20create%20an%20online%20version%20of%20%26quot%3BSelling%20Sunset%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20horological%20set.%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20go%20behind%20closed%20doors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarrer%20had%20met%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdarby_mcvay%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMcVay%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20girlfriend%2C%20Liz%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Flizztayylorr%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGuilliams%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20tatted-up%20couple%20who%20filmed%20local%20influencers%20and%20fitness%20models%2C%20through%20a%20model%20he'd%20been%20dating.%20Guilliams%2C%20who%20became%20Farrer's%20personal%20assistant%2C%20thought%20he%20had%20a%20flair%20for%20making%20his%20geeky%20hobby%20seem%20cool.%20%26quot%3BHe%20talks%20about%20it%20like%20how%20a%20sneakerhead%20talks%20about%20shoes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BHe%20just%20breaks%20it%20down%20in%20a%20way%20that%20makes%20it%20cool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222656%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farrer%20taking%20a%20sip%20out%20of%20a%20whiskey%20glass%20while%20also%20having%20multiple%20watches%20on%20his%20arm%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65942fe0ab6f2ebb11f81ac1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222921%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20position%20myself%20to%20the%20right-hand%20side%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Farrer%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20they%20could%20see%20my%20watch.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ERichard%20Chance%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20YouTube%20series%2C%20the%20camera%20follows%20Farrer%20as%20he%20explains%20the%20tricks%20of%20the%20trade%20and%20luxuriates%20in%20the%20watch-mogul%20lifestyle%20%E2%80%94%20dropping%20%2418%2C000%20at%20one%20of%20Salt%20Bae's%20restaurants%2C%20zipping%20around%20Dallas%20in%20a%20black%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOwmv4bqldgs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELamborghini%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20combination%20of%20insider%20insights%20and%20luxury%20living%20proved%20intoxicating%3B%20before%20long%2C%20the%20Timepiece%20Gentleman%20channel%20had%20more%20than%20110%2C000%20subscribers.%20And%20the%20more%20attention%20Farrer%20got%2C%20the%20more%20he%20wanted.%20%26quot%3BI%20spent%2015%20hours%20a%20day%20on%20social%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20made%20a%20post%2C%20I%20would%20sit%20there%20for%20two%20hours%20and%20respond%20to%20every%20single%20comment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20timing%2C%20as%20it%20were%2C%20proved%20impeccable.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20crypto%20fortunes%20were%20starting%20to%20pour%20into%20the%20secondary%20watch%20market%2C%20generating%20a%20wealth%20of%20new%20customers.%20%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20young%20kids%20making%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Farrer%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20now%20they%20want%20to%20flex.%26quot%3B%20By%202021%2C%20he%20was%20pulling%20in%20%244%20million%20a%20month.%20He%20promised%20that%20customers%20would%20soon%20be%20able%20to%20purchase%20his%20watches%20at%20a%20storefront%20in%20Dallas%20%E2%80%94%20which%20already%20had%20his%20name%20frosted%20on%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20everyone%20was%20buying%20the%20Timepiece%20Gentleman's%20act.%20A%20real-estate%20developer%20and%20watch%20collector%20in%20Dallas%20who%20goes%20by%20his%20Reddit%20nickname%2C%20Crimepiece%2C%20recalls%20feeling%20highly%20suspicious%20of%20Farrer%20when%20he%20met%20him%20at%20a%20Starbucks%20to%20buy%20a%20watch.%20%26quot%3BI%20realized%20this%20guy%20doesn't%20know%20anything%20about%20watches%2C%26quot%3B%20Crimepiece%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20got%20a%20really%20creepy%20vibe%20from%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20seemed%20his%20suspicions%20were%20right.%20On%20June%2029%2C%202021%2C%20Farrer's%20social-media%20accounts%20suddenly%20all%20went%20dark.%20So%20did%20his%20storefront%2C%20down%20to%20the%20gilt%20logo%20that%20had%20been%20scraped%20off%20the%20door.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20headline%20on%20the%20trade%20site%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.watchcollectinglifestyle.com%2Fhome%2Fdallas-grey-watch-dealer-the-timepiece-gentleman-vanishes-with-millions-in-consignment-inventory%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWatch%20Collecting%20Lifestyle%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20confirmed%20everyone's%20fears%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Timepiece%20Gentleman%20Seems%20to%20Have%20Vanished%20with%20Millions%20of%20Dollars.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Blackout%2C%20as%20it%20came%20to%20be%20known%20among%20watch%20nerds%20on%20Reddit%2C%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20publicity%20stunt%20gone%20wrong.%20The%20idea%20had%20seemed%20novel%20to%20Farrer%3A%20Go%20dark%20for%20a%20week%20while%20working%20with%20local%20charities%2C%20then%20reopen%20to%20reveal%20the%20good%20work%20he'd%20done.%20Instead%2C%20people%20thought%20he'd%20stolen%20their%20cash%20and%20split.%20%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20people%20were%20going%20to%20talk%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Farrer%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20no%20idea%20it%20was%20going%20to%20happen%20so%20fast%20%E2%80%94%20or%20so%20negatively.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20well-known%20watch%20dealer%20who%20was%20horrified%20by%20the%20Blackout%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40RomanSharf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESharf%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20veteran%20watch%20dealer.%20%26quot%3BThe%20intent%20was%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20the%20execution%20was%20terrible.%26quot%3B%20A%20fast-talking%20Russian%20with%20an%20encyclopedic%20mind%20for%20horology%2C%20Sharf%20had%20become%20something%20of%20a%20godfather%20to%20Farrer%2C%20vouching%20for%20him%20to%20experienced%20dealers%20and%20appearing%20in%20his%20YouTube%20videos.%20But%20now%20he%20told%20his%20star%20pupil%20that%20he%20had%20violated%20the%20most%20important%20tenet%20of%20the%20gray-market%20watch%20business%3A%20trust.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20very%2C%20very%20small%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Farrer.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20one%20does%20reflects%20bad%20on%20others.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20Farrer%2C%20there%20was%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20bad%20press.%20%26quot%3BA%20bunch%20of%20dealers%20got%20mad%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20care%20about%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20world%20knew%20who%20we%20were%20after%20that.%20Everyone%20in%20the%20watch%20industry%20had%20now%20heard%20of%20our%20name.%26quot%3B%20Fueled%20by%20the%20attention%2C%20he%20began%20to%20see%20himself%20as%20the%20biggest%20name%20in%20luxury%20watches.%20%26quot%3BIt%20definitely%20boosted%20his%20ego%20to%20a%20dangerous%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20recalled%20McVay%2C%20the%20videographer.%20To%20teach%20others%20the%20tricks%20of%20the%20trade%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20generate%20a%20new%20source%20of%20revenue%20%E2%80%94%20Farrer%20began%20offering%20coaching%20courses%20online.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20like%20the%20bad%20boy%20of%20the%20watch%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Guilliams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ERiding%20high%20on%20the%20notoriety%20from%20the%20Blackout%2C%20Farrer%20decided%20to%20move%20his%20watch%20business%20to%20the%20most%20dazzling%20market%20of%20all%3A%20the%20celebrity-filled%20world%20of%20Los%20Angeles.%20In%20Dallas%2C%20it%20was%20tough%20to%20sell%20a%20watch%20for%20%24100%2C000.%20In%20LA%2C%20buyers%20routinely%20shelled%20out%20six%20figures%20for%20a%20single%20timepiece.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seemed%20like%20money%20was%20endless%20out%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Farrer%20said.%20Plus%2C%20the%20sushi%20was%20to%20die%20for.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20Nobu%20Malibu%20for%20lunch%20to%20sell%20a%20watch%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20making%2010%20grand%2C%20and%20then%20we're%20driving%20over%20to%20Santa%20Monica%20right%20by%20the%20beach%2C%20sell%20another%20watch%2C%20have%20another%20sushi%20somewhere%20else.%26quot%3B%20He%20rented%20what%20was%20billed%20as%20the%20most%20expensive%20apartment%20in%20town%2C%20a%2019%2C000-square-foot%2C%20two-level%20penthouse%20complete%20with%20a%20rock-climbing%20wall%2C%20three%20bars%2C%20and%20a%20panoramic%20view%20of%20the%20city%20%E2%80%94%20the%20fantasy%20apartment%20he'd%20always%20imagined%20the%20Timepiece%20Gentleman%20living%20in.%20He%20told%20a%20local%20real-estate%20magazine%20that%20he%20planned%20to%20put%20a%20million%20dollars%20into%20the%20place%20to%20add%20a%20spa%2C%20a%20sauna%2C%20and%20four%20outdoor%20lounges%2C%20each%20boasting%20a%20different%20landscape.%20%26quot%3BA%20purveyor%20of%20luxury%20goods%20is%20bringing%20Texas-sized%20ambitions%20to%20Downtown%20Los%20Angeles%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftherealdeal.com%2Fla%2F2022%2F03%2F09%2Fdtla-penthouse-sniffs-record-amid-rarefied-air-at-95k-per-month%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emagazine%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20effused.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farrer%20sitting%20in%20his%20expensive%20apartment%20looking%20out%20the%20window%20while%20sitting%20on%20a%20stack%20of%20cashan%20drinking%20champagne%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6594305eab6f2ebb11f81afd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFarrer%20rented%20the%20most%20expensive%20apartment%20in%20LA%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20of%20place%20he'd%20always%20imagined%20the%20Timepiece%20Gentleman%20living%20in.%3Cp%3ERichard%20Chance%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20those%20inside%20Farrer's%20world%2C%20his%20ambitions%20%E2%80%94%20and%20numbers%20%E2%80%94%20didn't%20add%20up.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20get%20Ferraris%20and%20Lamborghinis%20selling%20watches%20with%20these%20slim%2C%20slim%20margins%2C%26quot%3B%20Crimepiece%20told%20me.%20Those%20around%20Farrer%20tried%20to%20warn%20him%20that%20his%20luxury%20lifestyle%20was%20unsustainable.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20told%20him%20it%20was%20stupid%2C%26quot%3B%20McVay%20recalled.%20But%20Farrer%20said%20he%20had%20received%20a%20million-dollar%20infusion%20from%20an%20anonymous%20investor%2C%20who%20featured%20prominently%20%E2%80%94%20through%20a%20Darth%20Vader-sounding%20voice%20changer%20%E2%80%94%20in%20various%20Timepiece%20Gentleman%20videos.%20Farrer%20raised%20millions%20more%20by%20selling%20his%20personal%20collection%20of%20watches%2C%20and%20he%20planned%20to%20rent%20out%20the%20penthouse%20for%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20his%20past%20caught%20up%20with%20him.%20Ever%20since%20the%20Blackout%2C%20Farrer%20watchers%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FTheTpGentleman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EReddit%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20digging%20into%20his%20personal%20history%2C%20looking%20for%20dirt%20on%20the%20man%20they%20derisively%20called%20Coach%2C%20for%20his%20hammy%20training%20videos.%20In%20March%202022%2C%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20his%2034th%20birthday%2C%20Farrer%20woke%20to%20a%20screenshot%20on%20Reddit%20of%20his%20shirtless%20ad%20from%20his%20rentmasseur.com%20days.%20There%20he%20was%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frentmasseur.com%2Ftravisbaker%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETravis%20Baker%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20advertising%20%26quot%3BSensual%20and%20Erotic%20massages%2C%26quot%3B%20flaunting%20his%20washboard%20abs%20and%20a%20plate%20of%20brisket%20strategically%20shielding%20his%20groin.%20The%20Redditor's%20caption%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20Speechless.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Farrer%2C%20however%2C%20shock%20quickly%20gave%20way%20to%20relief.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20almost%20like%20this%20weight%20lifted%20off%20my%20shoulder%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20secret%20I%20had%20in%20my%20life%20is%20out.%26quot%3B%20Before%20the%20Reddit%20post%2C%20Guilliams%20said%2C%20Farrer%20always%20seemed%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Brobot%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20quality%20he%20himself%20admits%20to.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20very%20good%20at%20suppressing%20emotion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20But%20after%20the%20massage%20ad%20hit%20the%20internet%2C%20his%20vulnerability%20made%20him%20seem%20more%20human.%20%26quot%3BIf%20any%20of%20y'all%20like%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20his%20team%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20y'all%20don't%20want%20be%20my%20friend%20because%20of%20it%2C%20I%20totally%20understand.%26quot%3B%20Instead%2C%20Guilliams%20and%20McVay%20stuck%20by%20his%20side.%20Along%20with%20others%20on%20the%20team%2C%20they%20lived%20and%20worked%20in%20a%20sprawling%20house%20in%20the%20Hollywood%20Hills%20that%20Farrer%20was%20renting%20for%20%2450%2C000%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELate%20one%20night%2C%20as%20Guilliams%20was%20getting%20ready%20for%20bed%2C%20she%20saw%20something%20that%20terrified%20her.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20naked%20and%20putting%20lotion%20on%2C%20watching%20TV%20with%20my%20back%20to%20the%20window%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recalled%2C%20when%20she%20spotted%20someone%20standing%20in%20the%20garden%20and%20looking%20up%20at%20her.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20someone%20outside!%26quot%3B%20she%20screamed.%20When%20she%20and%20Farrer%20raced%20outside%2C%20they%20found%20the%20back%20gate%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20nights%20later%2C%20as%20Guilliams%20was%20watching%20TV%20in%20bed%20with%20McVay%2C%20they%20heard%20Farrer%20screaming%3A%20%26quot%3BHelp%20me!%20Wake%20up!%26quot%3B%20They%20found%20him%20shaking%20in%20his%20underwear%2C%20his%20hands%20and%20feet%20zip-tied.%20He%20told%20them%20he'd%20been%20woken%20by%20four%20men%20in%20black%2C%20pointing%20guns%20at%20him%20and%20demanding%20his%20watches.%20Farrer%20wasn't%20very%20secure%20about%20his%20inventory%3A%20Rather%20than%20locking%20his%20collection%20in%20a%20safe%20at%20night%2C%20he%20often%20kept%20his%20watches%20on%20display%20by%20his%20bed.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20like%20looking%20at%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%20Even%20after%20Guilliams%20spotted%20the%20stranger%20in%20the%20garden%2C%20Farrer%20kept%20%242.5%20million%20worth%20of%20watches%20in%20a%20briefcase%20behind%20his%20bed%2C%20next%20to%20his%20elliptical%20machine.%20Yet%20the%20thieves%2C%20miraculously%2C%20only%20made%20off%20with%20a%20single%20backpack%20that%20contained%20some%20%2430%2C000%20in%20watches%20and%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20robbery%2C%20by%20Farrer's%20standards%2C%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20good%20for%20business.%20The%20guy%20who'd%20just%20gotten%20valuable%20press%20for%20renting%20the%20city's%20priciest%20penthouse%20was%20now%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fktla.com%2Fnews%2Flocal-news%2Fresidents-held-at-gunpoint-in-hollywood-hills-west-home-invasion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elocal%20TV%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sporting%20a%20Timepiece%20Gentleman%20hat%20as%20he%20recounted%20the%20dramatic%20break-in.%20The%20intruders%20were%20never%20caught.%20Looking%20back%2C%20Guilliams%20wonders%20whether%20the%20whole%20thing%20was%20yet%20another%20publicity%20stunt%2C%20fueled%20by%20Farrer's%20bottomless%20need%20for%20attention.%20%26quot%3BHe%20wanted%20to%20be%20seen%20out%20here%20so%20bad%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Detectives%20investigating%20a%20break%20in%20while%20Farrer%20talks%20to%20the%20media%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65942f62ec62ab5daf7fee96%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222700%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFarrer%20lost%20%2430%2C000%20in%20the%20robbery%20%E2%80%94%20but%20some%20wondered%20if%20it%20was%20just%20another%20publicity%20stunt.%3Cp%3ERichard%20Chance%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20robbery%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20least%20of%20the%20Timepiece%20Gentlemen's%20problems.%20Not%20long%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20Farrer%20tried%20to%20unload%20his%20%24300%2C000%20Audemars%20Piguet%20Royal%20Oak%2C%20a%20dazzling%20white-gold%20chronograph%20frosted%20with%20a%20purple%20dial.%20Farrer%20had%20listed%20it%20for%20%24330%2C000%2C%20counting%20on%20making%20his%20usual%2010%25%20profit%20on%20the%20sale.%20But%20now%2C%20he%20discovered%2C%20he%20couldn't%20break%20even.%20He%20ended%20up%20taking%20a%20%24100%2C000%20hit%20on%20it%20instead.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20when%20I%20realized%20we're%20in%20deep%20shit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20April%202022%2C%20the%20luxury-watch%20bubble%20%E2%80%94%20inflated%20by%20the%20bizarre%20combination%20of%20COVID%20and%20crypto%20%E2%80%94%20suddenly%20burst.%20%26quot%3BIt%20had%20to%20pop%20sometime%2C%26quot%3B%20Farrer%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20think%20it%20would%20be%20then.%26quot%3B%20Farrer%20had%20been%20running%20a%20consignment%20business%2C%20reselling%20watches%20for%20clients%20and%20taking%20a%20commission%20of%205%25.%20But%20with%20the%20market%20plunging%20by%2020%25%2C%20Farrer%20began%20to%20panic.%20The%20day%20his%20probation%20ended%20on%20his%20DUI%20charge%2C%20he%20tossed%20away%20his%20ankle%20monitor%20and%20began%20to%20drink%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuilliams%20had%20never%20seen%20the%20person%20she%20calls%20%26quot%3BDrunk%20Anthony%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20monster%20was%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20obnoxious%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20gets%20this%20look%20and%20you%20can%20just%20tell%20tonight's%20going%20be%20a%20bad%20night.%26quot%3B%20The%20more%20vodkas%20he%20downed%2C%20the%20more%20money%20he%20blew%20on%20sports%20cars%2C%20Vegas%20gambling%2C%20and%20high-priced%20sex%20workers.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20start%20drinking%20and%20start%20spending%20and%20spending%20and%20spending%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20And%20he%20was%20funding%20it%2C%20he%20admits%2C%20in%20a%20way%20that%20sounds%20awfully%20close%20to%20the%20definition%20of%20a%20Ponzi%20scheme.%20%26quot%3BMy%20flaw%20was%20I%20was%20double-dipping%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BRather%20than%20me%20pay%20you%20back%20immediately%2C%20I%20would%20take%20that%20money%20and%20go%20buy%20more%20inventory%20and%20then%20try%20to%20sell%20that%20inventory%20really%20quick%20so%20I%20could%20actually%20make%20some%20money%20and%20then%20pay%20you%20out.%26quot%3B%20In%20other%20words%2C%20he'd%20sell%20your%20watch%20for%20you%20%E2%80%94%20but%20good%20luck%20getting%20your%20money%20back%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Farrer%20continued%20to%20post%20his%20sushi-loving%2C%20Lamborghini-driving%20videos%20online%2C%20the%20clients%20he%20was%20stiffing%20began%20to%20boil%20over.%20Wesley%20Stokes%2C%20who%20owned%20a%20plumbing%20company%20in%20South%20Carolina%2C%20had%20%242%20million%20worth%20of%20watches%20on%20consignment%20with%20Farrer%20when%20the%20payments%20suddenly%20stopped.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20going%20to%20sell%20them%20and%20he%20was%20going%20to%20keep%20a%20little%20commission%20in%20the%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20Stokes%20said%2C%20but%20instead%20%26quot%3Bhe%20pretty%20much%20sold%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20and%20never%20paid%20me.%26quot%3B%20Stokes%20sent%20an%20armored%20car%20to%20Farrer's%20office%20to%20get%20the%20cash%2C%20but%20came%20away%20empty-handed.%20%26quot%3BHe%20still%20owes%20me%20a%20million%2C%26quot%3B%20Stokes%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBob%20Schober%2C%20who%20owns%20a%20roofing%20company%20in%20Scottsdale%2C%20Arizona%2C%20had%20been%20a%20loyal%20Timepiece%20Gentleman%20customer%20since%20seeing%20Farrer%20sell%20Cleveland%20Browns%20cornerback%20Joe%20Haden%20a%20Richard%20Mille%20watch.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20this%20dude%20was%20legit%20completely%2C%26quot%3B%20Schober%20recalled.%20%26quot%3BYou%20couldn't%20have%20convinced%20me%20otherwise%20in%20the%20beginning.%26quot%3B%20But%20after%20the%20robbery%2C%20the%20market%20crash%2C%20and%20Farrer's%20incessant%20posturing%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Schober%20grew%20suspicious%20about%20the%20consignments%20the%20Timepiece%20Gentleman%20was%20holding%20for%20him.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20got%20200%20grand%20worth%20of%20my%20watches%2C%26quot%3B%20Schober%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20I'm%20hearing%20that%20he%20is%20not%20paying%20people%20money%20that%20he%20owes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20July%2C%20after%20Schober%20realized%20his%20watches%20were%20no%20longer%20listed%20on%20the%20TPG%20site%2C%20he%20called%20Farrer%20to%20confront%20him.%20Farrer%2C%20who%20had%20recently%20stayed%20at%20Schober's%20home%20after%20delivering%20a%20watch%2C%20considered%20him%20a%20friend.%20So%20he%20drunkenly%20confessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20just%20tell%20everyone%20straight%20up%20I'm%20%245%20million%20in%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Schober%20over%20the%20phone.%20%26quot%3BI've%20been%20a%20complete%20fucking%20degenerate.%20I%20got%20a%20little%20taste%20of%20success%20and%20the%20stars%2C%20and%20I%20thought%20that%20would%20never%20end.%20For%20the%20last%20few%20years%20that's%20how%20I've%20lived%20my%20life%20%E2%80%94%20that%20it%20would%20never%20end%2C%20that%20I%20was%20way%20too%20good%20at%20what%20I%20did.%20I%20was%20way%20too%20famous%2C%20way%20too%20popular.%20I%20was%20the%20leader%20of%20all%20this%20in%20the%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20let%20that%20all%20kind%20of%20tank%20me.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20claimed%20was%20%26quot%3Btoo%20smart%26quot%3B%20to%20get%20robbed%2C%20which%20fueled%20Schober's%20suspicions%20that%20the%20home%20break-in%20had%20been%20staged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20time%2C%20whatever%20relief%20Farrer%20felt%20from%20coming%20clean%20didn't%20last%20long.%20Schober%20had%20been%20secretly%20recording%20the%20call%2C%20and%20he%20posted%20all%2018%20minutes%20of%20it%20on%20TikTok%2C%20along%20with%20a%20warning%20to%20anyone%20else%20who%20did%20business%20with%20the%20Timepiece%20Gentleman.%20Then%20he%20went%20to%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20responding%20with%20contrition%20and%20offering%20to%20make%20things%20right%2C%20Farrer%20felt%20betrayed%20by%20Schober.%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20reason%20I%20told%20him%20was%20because%20I%20was%20so%20stressed%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20eating%20at%20me%20alive%20to%20the%20point%20I%20was%20drinking%20every%20night%2C%20not%20working%20out%2C%20eating%20like%20shit%2C%20not%20liking%20who%20I%20was%20becoming.%20I%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20dark%20hole.%20And%20I%20wanted%20someone%20I%20could%20tell%20it%20to%20for%20once%2C%20so%20I'm%20not%20holding%20it%20inside%20anymore%2C%20but%20also%20give%20me%20advice.%26quot%3B%20When%20he%20speed-dialed%20Schober%2C%20though%2C%20he%20discovered%20his%20number%20had%20been%20blocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20Farrer%20was%20a%20young%20foster%20kid%20in%20Texas%2C%20he'd%20been%20on%20the%20run%3A%20from%20his%20father%2C%20from%20the%20law%2C%20and%20mostly%20from%20himself.%20The%20few%20times%20the%20truth%20about%20his%20life%20had%20come%20out%2C%20he%20had%20felt%20unburdened%2C%20only%20to%20fuck%20everything%20up%20again.%20Last%20August%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20come%20as%20clean%20as%20whatever%20version%20of%20himself%20he%20had%20in%20his%20head%20would%20allow.%20Sitting%20in%20front%20of%20his%20sleek%20white%20kitchen%20cabinets%2C%20an%20empty%20paper%20towel%20roll%20in%20a%20stand%2C%20Farrer%20taped%20what%20he%20captioned%20his%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmKLFcjm83vY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERock%20Bottom%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20video%20for%20YouTube.%20For%2014%20minutes%20he%20described%20his%20addictions%2C%20his%20%245%20million%20debt%2C%20his%20lies.%20All%20he%20ever%20wanted%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20to%20be%20popular%20like%20those%20he%20envied%20on%20TV%20and%20the%20internet%2C%20and%20that%20had%20led%20to%20his%20all-consuming%20obsession%20with%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bthis%20flex%20lifestyle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20want%20people%20thinking%20I%20was%20a%20failure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20choking%20back%20tears.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20want%20people%20thinking%20I%20was%20a%20fraud%2C%20a%20fake.%20I've%20gotten%20accustomed%20to%20this%20lifestyle%20%E2%80%94%20and%20getting%20that%20type%20of%20attention%2C%20it%20ruined%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20night%20before%20the%20FBI%20arrested%20him%20in%20his%20storage%20locker%2C%20Farrer%20told%20me%20he%20wasn't%20guilty%20of%20anything%20more%20than%20being%20in%20debt.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20Ponzi%20scheme%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20insisted%20as%20we%20headed%20outside.%20%26quot%3BA%20Ponzi%20scheme%20is%20when%20you%20knowingly%20dupe%20Peter%20to%20pay%20Paul.%20I%20never%20did%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223177%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farrer%20in%20handcuffs%20made%20from%20watch%20straps%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65942eddec62ab5daf7fee1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222398%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20interviewing%2020%20of%20Farrer's%20clients%2C%20the%20FBI%20arrested%20him%20on%20a%20fraud%20charge%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20could%20send%20him%20to%20prison%20for%2020%20years.%3Cp%3ERichard%20Chance%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20disagreed.%20After%20interviewing%2020%20of%20Farrer's%20clients%2C%20including%20Schober%20and%20Stokes%2C%20federal%20agents%20arrested%20him%20on%20suspicion%20of%20wire%20and%20mail%20fraud%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Fcompliance%2Fcriminal-investigation%2Ffounder-of-beverly-hills-gentlemen-timepieces-consignment-store-charged-with-conning-victims-in-luxury-watch-ponzi-type-scheme%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Echarges%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20could%20send%20him%20to%20federal%20prison%20for%20up%20to%2020%20years.%20He%20is%20currently%20being%20held%2C%20without%20bail%2C%20in%20a%20federal%20jail%20in%20downtown%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20the%20city%20he%20came%20to%20conquer.%20He%20has%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20to%20the%20charges%3B%20his%20trial%20is%20scheduled%20for%20October%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20night%20before%20he%20was%20busted%2C%20as%20we%20walked%20past%20Gold's%20Gym%2C%20Farrer%20spoke%20optimistically%20about%20paying%20his%20customers%20back%20%E2%80%94%20starting%20with%20selling%20his%20Ducati%2C%20which%20was%20parked%20nearby.%20When%20I%20asked%20how%20confident%20he%20felt%20about%20making%20good%20on%20the%20%245%20million%2C%20he%20didn't%20hesitate.%20%26quot%3BTwo%20hundred%20percent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20only%20way%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20do%20it%20is%20if%20I%20die.%20Even%20if%20I%20go%20to%20prison%2C%20I'll%20get%20out%2C%20and%20I'll%20start%20where%20I%20left%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDown%20along%20the%20Venice%20Boardwalk%2C%20we%20passed%20other%20homeless%20people%20scouting%20spots%20for%20the%20evening.%20Farrer%20had%20packed%20a%20knife%2C%20just%20in%20case.%20He%20hoped%20to%20spend%20the%20night%20in%20a%20nearby%20lifeguard%20stand.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20being%20by%20the%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20gazing%20over%20the%20darkened%20beach.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20serenity%20like%20nothing%20else.%26quot%3B%20As%20we%20watched%20the%20waves%20on%20his%20last%20night%20as%20a%20free%20man%2C%20he%20told%20me%20he%20had%20already%20storyboarded%20his%20next%20YouTube%20series%3A%20his%20comeback.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20used%20to%20watching%20this%20guy%20who%20used%20to%20drive%20a%20Ferrari%20or%20a%20Lambo%20or%20a%20G-Wagen%2C%20and%20ate%20at%20nice%20restaurants%20and%20lived%20in%20the%20best%20places%2C%20but%20now%20he's%20sleeping%20in%20the%20dirt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20entertainment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fdavid-kushner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%