of%20a%20leader%20starts%20to%20look%20very%20different.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20is%20set%20to%20transform%20leaders%20as%20well%20as%20the%20people%20they%20manage.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExperts%20say%20that%20AI's%20impact%20could%20affect%20how%20leaders%20are%20measured.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOld%20metrics%20for%20their%20value%2C%20like%20budget%20or%20team%20size%2C%20may%20change%2C%20experts%20say.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20isn't%20just%20going%20to%20change%20your%20job%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20going%20to%20change%20your%20manager%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20studies%20have%20suggested%20AI%20can%20give%20average%20workers%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fusing-ai-like-chatgpt-will-make-you-more-successful-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebig%20productivity%20boost%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethere%20are%20indications%20that%20it%20won't%20simply%20automate%20jobs%20and%20replace%20human%20workers%2C%20but%20play%20a%20more%20complicated%20role%20in%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFabian%20Stephany%2C%20who%20lectures%20about%20AI%20at%20the%20Oxford%20Internet%20Institute%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20was%20having%20a%20more%20%26quot%3Bambiguous%20role%20in%20the%20labor%20market%26quot%3B%20than%20simply%20causing%20jobs%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bautomated%20away%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bmass%20scale.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephany%20is%20among%20the%20experts%20who%20told%20BI%20that%20AI%20could%20affect%20your%20boss's%20job%20as%20much%20as%20yours%2C%20as%20AI%20makes%20skills%20%E2%80%94%20not%20scale%20%E2%80%94%20the%20benchmark%20by%20which%20workplace%20leaders%20are%20judged%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%2C%20he%20added%2C%20is%20influencing%20the%20workplace%20at%20%26quot%3Bthe%20task%20and%20skill%20level.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIt%20comes%20down%20to%20augmenting%20and%20automating%20certain%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20changes%20brought%20by%20AI%20dovetail%20with%20ongoing%20changes%20in%20how%20companies%20approach%20leadership%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-working-to-live-rather-than-living-to-work-2024-1%3Fmrfhud%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cu%3ERavin%20Jesuthasan%2C%20a%20global%20leader%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20transformation%20services%20at%20consulting%20giant%20Mercer%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompanies%20are%20already%20starting%20to%20rewrite%20the%20rules%20of%20leadership%2C%20rewrite%20the%20rules%20of%20management%2C%20and%20reward%20managers%20for%20different%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Cu%3EJesuthasan%3C%2Fu%3E%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20a%20worker's%20seniority%20reflected%20the%20size%20of%20their%20team%20and%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20AI%20on%20the%20scene%2C%20it%20won't%20so%20much%20reflect%20salaries%20and%20budgets%2C%20but%20employers%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20gonna%20actually%20reward%20you%20for%20your%20impact%20on%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Jesuthasan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20AI%20restructures%20people's%20workloads%20and%20makes%20individual%20workers%20more%20productive%2C%20EY's%20global%20chief%20technology%20officer%20Nicola%20Morini%20Bianzino%20told%20BI%2C%20metrics%20like%20the%20number%20of%20direct%20reports%20or%20budget%20size%20may%20no%20longer%20be%20adequate%20measures%20of%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20basically%20need%20to%20turn%20around%20the%20way%20you%20look%20at%20the%20discipline%20of%20management%20in%20general%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20about%20doing%20something%20that%20I%20was%20doing%20yesterday%20more%20efficiently.%20This%20is%20about%20doing%20something%20completely%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bu