20be%20informed%20by%20the%20court%20that%20which%20are%20the%20matters%20in%20which%20we%20can%20approach%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20in%20which%20matters%20we%20should%20not.%20Because%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20we%20file%20such%20a%20plea%20whether%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20admit%20it%20or%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sibal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20M.M.%20Sundresh%2C%20and%20Bela%20M.%20Trivedi%20on%20February%202%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-hemant-soren-jharkhand-high-court%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edirected%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20writ%20petition%20to%20be%20moved%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20high%20court%20and%20asked%20Sibal%2C%20who%20is%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20counsel%2C%20as%20to%20why%20the%20matter%20cannot%20be%20heard%20by%20the%20lower%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20courts%20are%20open%20to%20everybody.%20Second%2C%20high%20courts%20are%20constitutional%20courts.%20If%20we%20permit%20one%20person%20to%20come%20here%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20allow%20everyone%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Khanna%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F4aon_ARlHLY%3Fsi%3DhMwjXtJWk-VRfzvg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoren%E2%80%99s%20plea%20came%20up%20after%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20on%20Thursday%20had%20agreed%20to%20list%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20petition%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoren%20had%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20high%20court%20challenging%20the%20ED%20arrest%20but%20when%20he%20filed%20a%20similar%20petition%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Sibal%20undertook%20that%20he%20would%20withdraw%20the%20high%20court%20petition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20Article%2032%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20which%20states%20that%20individuals%20have%20the%20right%20to%20approach%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20enforcement%20of%20other%20fundamental%20rights%20recognised%20by%20the%20constitution%2C%20Sibal%20said%20that%20the%20apex%20court%20must%20make%20a%20policy%20under%20which%20the%20public%20should%20know%20when%20to%20approach%20the%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20there%20would%20hardly%20have%20been%20any%20such%20instance%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India%20when%20a%20sitting%20chief%20minister%20is%20arrested%20and%20that%20is%20also%20not%20deserving%20to%20be%20heard%20under%20Article%2032.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20different%20if%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20heard%20us%20and%20then%2C%20after%20hearing%20it%2C%20said%20%E2%80%98we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20interfere%20and%20go%20to%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99.%20But%20to%20tell%20us%20first%20that%20we%20should%20go%20to%20high%20court%20without%20hearing%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20Union%20government%2C%20Sibal%20said%20that%20the%20aim%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20opposition%20chief%20minister%20in%20any%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20will%20do%20this%20against%20%5BDelhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%5D%20Kejriwal.%20They%20want%20only%20double-engine%20governments%20and%20no%20opposition%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20what%20will%20happen%20is%20that%2010%20more%20cases%20will%20be%20slapped%20on%20Hemant%20Soren%20while%20in%20custody.%20All%20of%20them%20made-up%20cases%2C%20so%20that%20he%20does%20not%20come%20out%20of%20jail%20and%20which%20will%20benefit%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArrested%20in%20an%20alleged%20land%20scam%20case%2C%20Soren%20stepped%20down%20as%20chief%20minister%20late%20on%20January%2031.%20While%20leaders%20of%20his%20party%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20Janmukti%20Morcha%2C%20have%20noted%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20arrest%20%E2%80%93%20just%20before%20the%20general%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20and%20called%20it%20a%20brazen%20act%20of%20political%20vendetta%2C%20Soren%20had%20expressed%20fear%20that%20his%20arrest%20may%20allow%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20impose%20president%E2%80%99s%20rule%20in%20the%20state.%20He%20has%20also%20invoked%20the%20SC%2FST%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%20against%20ED%20officers%20for%20allegedly%20harassing%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESibal%20said%20that%20the%20matter%20relates%20to%202007%2C%20but%20the%20arrest%20took%20place%20in%202024.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20where%20will%20we%20go%3F%20What%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20country%3F%20What%20kind%20of%20politics%20is%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707044413000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02115438%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-must-make-policy-on-when-it-can-be-approached-sibal-on-hemant-sorens-plea%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20February%202%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20directed%20Soren%20through%20his%20counsel%20to%20approach%20the%20Jharkhand%20high%20court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-must