20like%20me%2C%20got%20off%20in%20La%20Romana%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20passengers%20were%20booked%20to%20stay%20the%20entire%2014%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20a%20Broadway%20fanatic%2C%20I%20love%20musicals%2C%20so%20the%20two%20shows%20were%20exactly%20what%20I'd%20see%20on%20a%20night%20out%20at%20home.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Stardust%20Theater%20with%20the%20lights%20on.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd146243bb77284ba306c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEach%20show%20played%20twice%20a%20night%2C%20which%20helped%20with%20the%20crowds.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20show%20was%20a%20sing-off%20style%20performance%2C%20while%20the%20other%20was%20a%20series%20of%20rock%20song%20covers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20no%20theater%20expert%2C%20but%20I%20personally%20thought%20the%20singers%20were%20incredible%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20dancers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20cruise%20director%2C%20Will%2C%20dancing%20along%20with%20the%20crew%20was%20quite%20entertaining%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20activities%20were%20mostly%20held%20in%20the%20lounges%20and%20bars%20scattered%20throughout%20the%20ship%2C%20while%20the%20shows%20were%20in%20the%20Stardust%20Theater.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20lobby%20of%20the%20Norwegian%20Sky%20with%20people%20around.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd14a443bb77284ba30721%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20lobby%20of%20the%20Norwegian%20Sky%20on%20embarkation%20day.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NCL%20Sky%20is%20small%2C%20so%20the%20lounges%20and%20social%20spaces%20are%20not%20as%20grandiose%20as%20other%20ships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lobby%20on%20the%20Sky%20is%20particularly%20tiny%2C%20which%20is%20the%20only%20area%20I%20found%20annoyingly%20crowded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFortunately%2C%20I%20never%20found%20myself%20fighting%20for%20a%20seat%20%E2%80%94%20which%20I%20do%20think%20is%20sometimes%20easier%20when%20you're%20solo%2C%20though.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223485%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sugarcane%20lounge%20with%20singers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd1e966fcb546d2d4ba389%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223022%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sugarcane%20lounge%2C%20which%20had%20a%20bar%2C%20was%20a%20great%20place%20to%20enjoy%20live%20music%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20day.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20sailing%20was%20apparently%20close%20to%20full%2C%20but%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20the%20crowd%20control%20even%20though%20there%20were%20up%20to%202%2C000%20guests%20onboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20always%20an%20open%20chair%20outside%2C%20and%20getting%20an%20elevator%20was%20typically%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20casino%2C%20spa%2C%20Starbucks%2C%20jewelry%20and%20alcohol%20stores%2C%20and%20a%20gift%20shop%20onboard.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20casino%20onboard%20had%20tables%20and%20machines.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd16a27a3d271488772268%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20cigarette%20smoke%20bothers%20you%2C%20I%20would%20avoid%20walking%20through%20the%20casino.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20these%20are%20an%20additional%20cost%2C%20though%20Starbucks%20can%20be%20included%20in%20the%20drink%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPersonally%2C%20I%20skipped%20the%20package%20because%20there's%20no%20way%20I%20could%20consume%20enough%20coffee%20and%20alcohol%20to%20justify%20the%20%24200%2B%20price%2C%20though%20I%20know%20plenty%20of%20people%20who%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EProbably%20the%20best%20part%20of%20cruising%20solo%20was%20there%20was%20nobody%20to%20hold%20me%20back%20from%20eating%20as%20much%20as%20I%20wanted.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Crossings%20Dining%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd19af43bb77284ba30d23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20were%20two%20dining%20rooms%2C%20but%20I%20liked%20the%20Crossings%20restaurant%20best.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20extremely%20busy%20at%20home%20when%20I'm%20not%20traveling%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20for%20sit-down%20meals%20or%20cooking%20and%20end%20up%20eating%20a%20lot%20of%20takeout%20%E2%80%94%20so%20the%20restaurant-grade%20food%20was%20a%20nice%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20was%20a%20buffet%2C%20free%20dining%20rooms%2C%20specialty%20restaurants%2C%20pizza%2C%20and%20a%20late-night%20pub.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Scallops%2C%20beef%20chili%20with%20fries%2C%20cut%20meat%2C%20and%20ravioli.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd18d643bb77284ba30c40%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221550%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20example%2C%20I%20had%20ravioli%20and%20scallops%20from%20the%20dining%20room%2C%20beef%20chili%20from%20the%20late-night%20pub%2C%20and%20meat%20cuts%20from%20the%20buffet.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20specialty%20restaurants%20cost%20extra%2C%20while%20the%20dining%20rooms%20have%20rotating%20menus%2C%20and%20you%20can%20order%20as%20many%20appetizers%2C%20entr%C3%A9es%2C%20and%20desserts%20as%20your%20heart%20desires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20buffet%20and%20restaurants%20have%20set%20hours%2C%20while%20the%20pub%20has%20food%20available%20nearly%20all%20night%2C%20opening%20at%206%20p.m.%20and%20closing%20at%203%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20enjoyed%20the%20buffet%20food%20between%20main%20meals%20and%20took%20advantage%20of%20the%20option%20to%20sit%20outside.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20buffer%20seating%20was%20indoor%20or%20outdoor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd1bda43bb77284ba30e2c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221545%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EViews%20of%20buffet%20seating.%20There%20were%20also%20tables%20along%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20pool%20deck.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20dining%20rooms%20were%20only%20available%20during%20breakfast%2C%20lunch%2C%20and%20dinner%20hours%2C%20but%20I%20could%20still%20eat%20in%20between%20because%20the%20buffet%20and%20pizza%20bar%20were%20open%20between%20noon%20and%204%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20may%20make%20me%20sound%20like%20a%20slob%2C%20but%20part%20of%20the%20fun%20of%20vacation%20is%20guilt-free%20eating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20did%20pay%20%2450%20extra%20for%20sushi%20and%20Sake%20at%20an%20a-la-carte%20specialty%20restaurant.%20The%20add-on%20meal%20wasn't%20worth%20it%2C%20though.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22My%20sushi%20rolls.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd272743bb77284ba31a9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20got%20a%20California%2C%20a%20dragon%20roll%2C%20and%20Sake.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sushi%20option%20was%20one%20of%20the%20cheaper%20specialty%20meals%20available%2C%20and%20I%20tried%20it%20just%20for%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20food%20was%20good%2C%20it%20wasn't%20worth%20the%20money%20when%20there%20were%20plenty%20of%20free%20meals%20all%20around%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20dining%20room%20definitely%20had%20the%20overall%20best%20food%20out%20of%20everywhere%20I%20ate.%20But%20the%20service%20was%20much%20slower.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BBQ%20pork%20and%20french%20fries%20with%20cole%20slaw.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd1ccb7a3d27148877274e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20BBQ%20pork%20and%20fries%20I%20got%20for%20lunch%20one%20day%20in%20the%20dining%20room.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20sure%20if%20slow%20service%20is%20common%20on%20cruise%20ships%2C%20but%20my%20food%20took%2045%20minutes%20on%20two%20separate%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20personally%20didn't%20mind%2C%20I%20enjoyed%20being%20in%20the%20restaurant%20and%20able%20to%20look%20out%20at%20the%20water.%20I%20regularly%20got%20a%20window%20table%2C%20which%20was%20nice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGranted%2C%20sitting%20alone%20in%20a%20sea%20of%20couples%20and%20families%20at%20mealtimes%20was%20a%20little%20awkward%20at%20first%2C%20but%20I%20quickly%20realized%20nobody%20cared.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22My%20lunchtime%20window%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd1c7443bb77284ba30ecc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20lunchtime%20window%20table%20during%20the%20at-sea%20day.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20cruise%20lines%20with%20scheduled%20dining%20will%20sometimes%20put%20solo%20travelers%20at%20the%20same%20table%20as%20strangers%20in%20the%20dining%20rooms%2C%20which%20is%20not%20something%20I'd%20be%20comfortable%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20NCL's%20freestyle%20dining%20because%20I%20could%20go%20to%20the%20restaurant%20anytime%20I%20wanted%2C%20not%20at%20a%20set%20time.%20This%20meant%20I%20could%20get%20my%20own%20table%20and%20not%20have%20to%20navigate%20any%20social%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20one%20thing%20I%20didn't%20do%20was%20spend%20much%20time%20by%20the%20pool.%20I'm%20also%20not%20interested%20in%20the%20deck%20parties%20or%20gambling.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20pool%20deck%20on%20the%20Norwegian%20Sky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd1d3243bb77284ba30fa5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20family%20pool%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20boat%2C%20but%20it%20was%20small%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20kids.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20walked%20around%20the%20pool%20deck%20when%20I%20wanted%20some%20fresh%20air%20or%20to%20read%2C%20but%20I've%20never%20been%20a%20pool%20person.%20And%20I%20don't%20consider%20myself%20a%20party%20animal%20or%20a%20big%20drinker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20all%20fine.%20There%20was%20plenty%20of%20other%20stuff%20that%20interested%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThat's%20one%20of%20the%20best%20things%20about%20cruises%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20something%20for%20several%20different%20types%20of%20travelers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author's%20book%20and%20Heineken%20beer.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd15676fcb546d2d4b9b45%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20parked%20myself%20at%20a%20lounge%20one%20afternoon%20and%20just%20read%20and%20enjoyed%20a%20%247%20beer.%20The%20price%20wasn't%20as%20steep%20as%20I%20expected.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECruise%20ships%20have%20to%20cater%20to%20people%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20genders%2C%20and%20personalities%2C%20and%20I%20think%20Norwegian%20did%20a%20good%20job%20despite%20having%20less%20living%20space%20to%20work%20with%20on%20the%20Sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20far%20as%20ports%2C%20the%20cruise%20only%20had%20one%20stop%20in%20a%20coastal%20city%20called%20Puerto%20Plata%20on%20the%20northern%20side%20of%20the%20Dominican%20Republic.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20port%20was%20called%20Taino%20Bay.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd28317a3d27148877335d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoyal%20Caribbean's%20bigger%20Explorer%20of%20the%20Seas%20blocks%20the%20Norwegian%20Sky%20in%20this%20photo.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one-way%20cruise%20left%20Miami%20on%20Friday%2C%20had%20an%20at-sea%20day%20on%20Saturday%2C%20was%20in%20port%20most%20of%20Sunday%2C%20and%20disembarked%20on%20Monday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPassengers%20could%20either%20book%20an%20excursion%2C%20stay%20on%20the%20ship%2C%20or%20relax%20in%20the%20port.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20lazy%20river%20in%20the%20cruise%20port.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd1f9e43bb77284ba31241%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20river%20and%20pool%20were%20free.%20Note%3A%20The%20ship%20in%20the%20background%20is%20Royal%20Caribbean%2C%20which%20shared%20the%20port%20with%20NCL%20that%20day.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20port%20had%20pools%2C%20a%20beach%2C%20restaurants%2C%20a%20bar%2C%20shopping%2C%20and%20even%20a%20lazy%20river%2C%20all%20a%20short%20walk%20from%20the%20boat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20looked%20really%20nice%2C%20actually%2C%20and%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20time%20to%20explore%20this%20area%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20wanted%20to%20see%20some%20of%20the%20island%20while%20I%20was%20there%2C%20and%20I%20had%20a%20%2450%20excursion%20credit%2C%20so%20I%20booked%20a%20zipline%20and%20waterfall%20tour%20through%20NCL.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20holding%20her%20excursion%20ticket.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd1f0f6fcb546d2d4ba421%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENCL%20left%20my%20excursion%20ticket%20in%20my%20room%20on%20embarkation%20day.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBooking%20an%20excursion%20with%20the%20cruise%20line%20will%20ensure%20you%20get%20back%20to%20the%20boat%20on%20time.%20If%20you%20go%20out%20and%20about%20on%20your%20own%2C%20make%20sure%20to%20watch%20the%20clock%2C%20or%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2-cruise-ship-passengers-stranded-on-dock-after-missing-departure-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eship%20could%20leave%20without%20you%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tour%20took%20me%20into%20the%20mountainous%20area%20of%20the%20island%2C%20which%20is%20more%20my%20style%20since%20I%20love%20hiking%20and%20adventurous%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHere%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20socialize%20a%20bit%20with%20the%20other%20travelers%20after%20keeping%20to%20myself%20most%20of%20the%20at-sea%20day%2C%20and%20I'm%20glad%20I%20did.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20on%20the%20hike%20next%20to%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20jump%20into%20the%20water.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd21587a3d271488772cc5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221552%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20excursion%20also%20included%20some%20cliff%20jumping%2C%20which%20I%20wasn't%20expecting%20but%20still%20enjoyed.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20group%20was%20about%2025%20people%2C%20so%20I%20was%20kind%20of%20forced%20to%20chat.%20I'm%20glad%20I%20did%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20loved%20meeting%20the%20locals%2C%20who%20were%20great%20tour%20guides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20ended%20up%20making%20friends%20with%20another%20cruisegoer%2C%20and%20we%20actually%20went%20to%20dinner%20and%20a%20show%20together%20that%20night.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22On%20the%20ride%20back%20from%20the%20excursion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd21f47a3d271488772d7e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20downside%20of%20cruises%20is%20that%20there%20is%20limited%20time%20to%20see%20the%20ports.%20I%20wish%20I%20could've%20explored%20Puerto%20Plata%20more.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20reason%20I%20love%20solo%20traveling%2C%20in%20general%2C%20is%20all%20of%20the%20interesting%20people%20I%20meet.%20And%20I'm%20happy%20the%20cruise%20was%20no%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMeeting%20her%20was%20a%20nice%20relief%20after%20an%20underwhelming%20solo%20meetup%20on%20the%20first%20night.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223848%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Overlooking%20the%20ship%20at%20night.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd22526fcb546d2d4ba709%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222886%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20I%20got%20to%20the%20meetup%20spot%2C%20there%20wasn't%20any%20clear%20indication%20of%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20group%20and%20who%20wasn't.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENCL%20puts%20a%20daily%20solo%20meetup%20on%20the%20schedule.%20I%20went%20the%20first%20night%2C%20but%20it%20was%20awkward%2C%20with%20no%20clear%20indication%20of%20who%20was%20solo%20or%20any%20type%20of%20icebreaker%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20may%20have%20just%20been%20my%20experience%2C%20though.%20My%20new%20friend%20said%20she%20had%20a%20great%20time%20at%20a%20solo%20meetup%20on%20a%20previous%20NCL%20cruise%20to%20Alaska.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20I%20ended%20up%20liking%20the%20boat%20more%20than%20the%20port%20%E2%80%94%20which%20I%20think%20is%20the%20main%20draw%20for%20many%20cruise%20lovers%2C%20anyway.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222749%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20the%20bars.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd22b97a3d271488772e1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222757%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bars%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20places%20that%20was%20hard%20to%20find%20seating%2C%20but%20the%20bartenders%20were%20quick%20with%20drinks.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20personally%20like%20cruising%20because%20of%20the%20opportunity%20to%20explore%20the%20boat%20and%20go%20to%20the%20shows%20and%20events.%20The%20concept%20just%20allures%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20days%20were%20spent%20getting%20up%20early%20and%20going%20to%20the%20gym%2C%20participating%20in%20the%20day%20and%20evening%20events%2C%20and%20going%20to%20bed%20by%2010%3A30%20p.m.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20gym%20with%20treadmills.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd23377a3d271488772e9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20gym%20was%20empty%20when%20I%20took%20this%20photo%20right%20after%20boarding%2C%20but%20it%20was%20pretty%20busy%20when%20I%20went%20the%20next%20morning.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20definitely%20needed%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20my%20morning%20workout%2C%20given%20how%20much%20I%20was%20eating.%20The%20gym%20was%20a%20good%20size%20and%20overlooked%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt's%20exactly%20how%20I%20wanted%20to%20spend%20my%20weekend%20cruise%2C%20and%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20fun%20doing%20what%20I%20wanted%20%E2%80%94%20there%20was%20no%20one%20I%20had%20to%20accommodate.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20of%20the%20author%20off%20the%20back%20of%20the%20ship.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd23ca43bb77284ba31713%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20thing%20I%20love%20doing%20is%20just%20walking%20around%20the%20side%20of%20the%20boat%20and%20listening%20to%20music%20or%20podcasts.%20It's%20relaxing%20for%20me.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20travel%20alone%2C%20I%20love%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20compromise%20with%20anyone%20on%20what%20to%20do%20or%20where%20to%20eat.%20Simply%2C%20there's%20no%20drama.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20early%20bedtime%20meant%20I%20missed%20the%20evening%20comedy%2C%20karaoke%2C%20and%20parties.%20But%20I%20don't%20really%20regret%20getting%20extra%20sleep.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20comedian%20A-Train.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd24086fcb546d2d4ba865%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA-Train%20did%20a%20show%20on%20the%20first%20night%2C%20which%20was%20easily%20a%20highlight.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20comedy%20headliner%20was%20named%20A-Train%2C%20and%20I%20saw%20his%20first%20act%20on%20Friday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20truly%20hilarious%2C%20and%20I%20was%20a%20little%20bummed%20I%20missed%20his%20adult%20comedy%20on%20Saturday%20night%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20was%20playing%20at%2011%20p.m.%2C%20and%20that%20was%20just%20too%20late%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPlus%2C%20my%20inside%20cabin%20made%20sleeping%20easy%20because%20it%20was%20completely%20blackout.%20I%20think%20this%20could%20bother%20some%20people%2C%20but%20I%20loved%20it.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22My%20inside%20cabin%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd24847a3d27148877302c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20room%20was%20tiny%20but%20perfect%20for%20one%20person%20even%20though%20its%20intended%20for%20two%20%E2%80%94%20that%20would%20be%20a%20tight%20squeeze.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-rooms-windows-balconies-not-worth-it-frequent-cruiser-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einside%20cabin%20was%20the%20cheapest%20option%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20for%20the%20short%20trip%2C%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20spend%20another%20few%20hundred%20to%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20happy%20I%20didn't%20because%20I%20slept%20so%20well%2C%20and%20I'll%20keep%20booking%20an%20inside%20cabin%20on%20future%20cruises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPlus%2C%20unlike%20solo%20trips%20to%20other%20countries%2C%20this%20all-inclusive%20trip%20meant%20all%20my%20entertainment%20and%20food%20was%20pre-paid%20and%20pre-planned.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20at-sea%20day%20itinerary.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd24d66fcb546d2d4ba95b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20itinerary%20included%20times%20and%20places%20for%20each%20activites.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20all-inclusive%20aspect%20is%20the%20biggest%20difference%20between%20solo%20cruising%20and%20hostel-hopping%20in%20places%20like%20Eastern%20Europe%2C%20which%20is%20where%20I%20spent%20my%20early%2020s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20liked%20that%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20food%2C%20excursions%2C%20and%20hotel%20%E2%80%94%20was%20already%20paid%20for%20when%20I%20boarded%2C%20minus%20the%20few%20beers%20I%20ended%20up%20buying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGranted%2C%20the%20Sky%20has%20just%20the%20basic%20expectations%20and%20lacks%20the%20water%20slides%2C%20go-karts%2C%20and%20malls%20present%20on%20many%20modern%20ships.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Royal%20Caribbean%20and%20NCL%20ships%20side%20by%20side%20in%20port.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd25a643bb77284ba318cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20of%20the%20Norwegian%20Sky%20(left)%20next%20to%20Royal%20Caribbean's%20Explorer%20of%20the%20Seas%20(right)%2C%20which%20has%20been%20upgraded%20with%20slides.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20docked%20next%20to%20a%20giant%20Royal%20Caribbean%20ship%20with%20slides%20and%20other%20amenities%20poking%20out%20of%20its%20deck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPersonally%2C%20I%20think%20the%20Sky%20is%20perfect%20for%20three%20or%20so%20days.%20I%20probably%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20stay%20for%20the%20next%2011.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Basketball%20court.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd1a4b7a3d27148877259b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20sports%2C%20we%20had%20this%20court%20for%20things%20like%20soccer%20and%20basketball.%20There%20was%20also%20shuffleboar