the%20committee%20to%20regulate%20such%20lectures%20decided%20to%20call%20it%20off%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20its%20delivery%20on%20January%2031.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20is%20an%20excerpt%20from%20it.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20present%20century%20is%20often%20described%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98knowledge%20century%E2%80%99.%20We%20cannot%20be%20sure%20if%20this%20tag%20will%20stay%20valid%20until%20the%20end%20of%20the%20century%20or%20whether%20future%20historians%20will%20characterise%20this%20period%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Age%20of%20Knowledge%E2%80%99%20as%20has%20been%20the%20case%20with%20the%20Dark%20Ages%20or%20the%20Age%20of%20Reason%20in%20the%20past.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20the%20description%20sums%20up%20the%20euphoria%20resulting%20from%20the%20information%20explosion%20and%20the%20technologies%20surrounding%20the%20exponential%20growth%20in%20the%20information%20generated%20every%20passing%20second.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20this%20epithet%20may%20not%20be%20sufficiently%20adequate%20for%20characterizing%20our%20time.%20The%20century%20has%20also%20been%20forecast%20to%20be%20the%20era%20of%20water%20wars%2C%20an%20age%20of%20deathless%20humans%2C%20an%20epoch%20of%20ecological%20termination%2C%20and%20the%20moment%20for%20an%20irreversible%20merger%20of%20the%20physical%20and%20the%20digital.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%E2%80%98knowledge%20century%E2%80%99%20label%20is%20open%20to%20discussion%20and%20is%20not%20incontestable.%20Indeed%2C%20self-perceptions%20of%20human%20civilizations%20can%20change%20quite%20radically%20over%20a%20relatively%20short%20temporal%20span.%20But%20if%20at%20all%2C%20the%20present%20century%20can%20be%20viewed%20as%20a%20unique%20era%20in%20human%20history%2C%20marking%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20engagement%20with%20what%20is%20considered%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20would%20be%20interesting%20to%20reflect%20on%20where%20India%20stands%20in%20relation%20to%20this%20new%20turn%20in%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20it%20cannot%20be%20said%20with%20any%20certainty%20for%20want%20of%20the%C2%A0%20census%20that%20was%20to%20take%20place%20in%202021%2C%20perhaps%20India%20has%20already%C2%A0%20surpassed%20China%E2%80%99s%20population%20level.%20Also%2C%20the%20demographic%20proportion%20of%20the%20younger%20population%20in%20India%20at%20present%20is%20the%20largest%20ever%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%20with%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20population%20below%20the%20age%20of%2025.%20Of%20the%20entire%20global%20population%2C%20nearly%20one%20in%20every%2012%20humans%20is%20a%20young%20Indian%20for%20whom%20meaningful%20education%20is%20the%20most%20assured%20means%20of%20finding%20a%20decent%20livelihood.%20Education%2C%20knowledge%20production%20and%20research%20leading%20to%20widening%20of%20the%20horizons%20of%20thought%20and%20imagination%2C%20therefore%2C%20ought%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20important%20concerns%20of%20our%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EConsiderations%20of%20how%20and%20how%20much%20knowledge%20is%20produced%2C%20how%20it%20is%20transacted%20and%20how%20it%20is%20responding%20to%20social%20inequalities%20and%20ecological%20disconnect%20add%20to%20the%20vastness%20and%20complexities%20involved%20in%20a%20study%20of%20knowledge%20and%20education%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHaving%20spent%20close%20to%20half%20a%20century%20in%20and%20around%20universities%2C%20and%20having%20elsewhere%20presented%20academic%20research%20and%20essays%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20not%20too%20inappropriate%20to%20present%20my%20observations%20on%20the%20theme%20through%20a%20reflective%20statement.%20I%20do%20not%20intend%20to%20present%20a%20position%20or%20positions%20in%20it.%20Quite%20often%2C%20analytical%20studies%20have%20a%20purely%20subjective%20weave%20as%20their%20flip%20side%2C%20a%20tacit%20class-bias%20presented%20as%20%E2%80%98objective%E2%80%99%20culture-critique.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20the%20extent%20possible%2C%20I%20have%20avoided%20such%20analysis.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20would%20therefore%20like%20to%20describe%20this%20lecture%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98reflections%E2%80%99%20of%20a%20person%20for%20whom%20knowledge%20and%20education%20have%20been%20serious%20concerns%20for%20several%20decades.%20When%20I%20began%20working%20as%20a%20young%20researcher%20in%20literary%20studies%20in%20the%20early%20post-Independence%20years%2C%20the%20colonial%20experience%20was%20the%20obsessive%20interest%20of%20the%20day.%20Most%20forms%20of%20formal%20knowledge%2C%20scientific%20disciplines%20and%20social%20sciences%20were%20seen%20as%20having%20originated%20in%20the%20colonial%20%E2%80%98transfer%20of%20knowledge%E2%80%99.%20Scholarly%20debates%20revolved%20around%20the%20question%20of%20acceptance%20or%20rejection%20of%20these%20forms%20of%20knowledge.%20These%20debates%20were%20happening%20in%20several%20disciplines%2C%20if%20not%20all%20of%20them%2C%20ranging%20from%20history%20to%20literature%2C%20architecture%20to%20aesthetics%3B%20but%20invariably%20the%20reference%20point%20was%20the%20knowledge%20of%20the%20colonial%20mind.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%201980s%2C%20the%20interest%20started%20shifting%20to%20discussion%20of%20disparities%20inherent%20in%20every%20intellectual%20transaction%20between%20the%20colonizing%20Western%20cultures%20and%20the%20post-colonial%20societies.%20These%20discussions%20were%20fascinating%20and%20produced%20several%20works%20of%20great%20brilliance.%20They%20gained%20in%20significance%20as%20similar%20discussions%20had%20been%20taking%20place%20in%20other%20post-colonial%20cultures.%20In%20Western%20intellectual%20circles%20too%20colonialism%20and%20post-colonialism%20acquired%20as%20much%20centrality%20as%20the%20Cold%20War%20and%20imperialism%20had%20enjoyed%20earlier.%20I%20have%20chosen%20to%20overlook%20in%20this%20address%20many%20of%20the%20valuable%20insights%20generated%20over%20the%20decades%20in%20both%20these%20phases%20as%20they%20are%20by%20now%20well-settled%20in%20the%20arena%20of%20the%20history%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eof%20cultural%20relations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fslack-imgs-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There%20are%20many%20different%20ways%20to%20approach%20the%20thorny%20issue%20of%20decolonising%20knowledge.%20Credit%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221356%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-143400%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22668%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20witnessed%20rapidly%20sinking%20fortunes%20of%20%E2%80%98natural%20memory%E2%80%99%2C%20technology%20of%20knowledge%20incubation%20and%20knowledge%20reception%2C%20and%20the%20sanitisation%20of%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20effected%20through%20several%20exclusions.%20Photo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%2C%20however%2C%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20enormous%20amount%20of%20descriptive%20and%20analytical%20studies%20that%20those%20two%20moves%20produced%2C%20both%20within%20India%20and%20outside%2C%20I%20begin%20by%20briefly%20alluding%20to%20some%20of%20the%20iconic%20period-statements%20in%20the%20next%20section%2C%20before%20moving%20to%20the%20discussion%20of%20the%20more%20contemporary%2C%20and%20no%20less%20significant%20phenomena%20having%20a%20profound%20bearing%20on%20the%20question%20of%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20and%20education%20in%20India.%20These%20phenomena%20include%20the%20rapidly%20sinking%20fortunes%20of%20%E2%80%98natural%20memory%E2%80%99%2C%20technology%20of%20knowledge%20incubation%20and%20knowledge%20reception%2C%20and%20the%20sanitisation%20of%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20effected%20through%20several%20exclusions%20%E2%80%93%20linguistic%2C%20ethnic%20and%20epistemic.%20This%20book%2C%20therefore%2C%20reflects%20on%20the%20condition%20and%20crisis%20of%20knowledge%20as%20much%20as%20it%20is%2C%20by%20implication%2C%20about%20the%20condition%20and%20crisis%20of%20our%20democracy.%20In%20order%20to%20analyse%20the%20present%20status%20of%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20in%20India%20and%20the%20problems%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20higher%20education%2C%20this%20lecture%20will%20focus%20on%20four%20important%20elements%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20in%20Indian%20tradition(s)%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecond%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20trajectory%20of%20%E2%80%98memory%E2%80%99%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThird%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20patterns%20of%20social%20exclusion%20and%20their%20effect%20on%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20construction%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20%3Cstrong%3Efinally%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20technology%20on%20the%20forms%20of%20knowledge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20ancient%20civilisation%2C%20with%20amazing%20wealth%20of%20philosophical%2C%20literary%20and%20scientific%20treatises%20and%20unparalleled%20continuity%20of%20%E2%80%98the%20life%20of%20the%20mind%E2%80%99%2C%20India%20nonetheless%20was%20not%20at%20its%20most%20creative%20when%20the%20colonial%20scholars%20started%20exploring%20Indian%20thought%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%2018th%20century.%20Besides%2C%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20complicated%20reasons%2C%20the%20creative%20springs%20of%20ideas%20and%20imagination%20current%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebhashas%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20that%20time%20were%20not%20found%20to%20be%20of%20sufficient%20interest%20by%20the%20colonial%20English%20officers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheir%20focus%20remained%20almost%20entirely%20on%20literature%20and%20the%20texts%20in%20Sanskrit%20and%20Persian.%20Given%20the%20context%20of%20political%20domination%2C%20even%20a%20rather%20casual%20compliment%20from%20Goethe%20for%20the%20imaginative%20power%20of%20Kalidasa%E2%80%99s%20play%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShakuntalam%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eappeared%20to%20the%20Indian%20mind%20as%20great%20a%20victory%20as%2C%20a%20century%20later%2C%20the%20Nobel%20Prize%20in%20Literature%20for%20Rabindranath%20Tagore.%20During%20that%20one%20and%20a%20quarter%20century%20%E2%80%93%20from%20the%20founding%20of%20the%20Asiatic%20Society%20in%20the%201780s%20to%20the%20beginning%20of%20World%20War%20I%20and%20the%20struggle%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%20%E2%80%93%20any%20compliment%20from%20a%20European%20scholar%20was%20generally%20hugely%20overvalued%2C%20reflecting%20India%E2%80%99s%20complete%20loss%20of%20cultural%20self-confidence.%20Hence%2C%20the%20generous%20praise%20that%20Friedrich%20Max%20M%C3%BCller%20lavished%20on%20Indian%20thought%20was%20received%20by%20the%20Brahminical%20classes%20with%20ecstasy.%20He%20stated%20in%20a%20lecture%20to%20the%20Indian%20Civil%20Service%20aspirants%20in%20London%3A%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20were%20asked%20under%20what%20sky%20the%20human%20mind%20has%20most%20fully%20developed%20some%20of%20its%20choicest%20gifts%2C%20has%20most%20deeply%20pondered%20over%20the%20greatest%20problems%20of%20life%2C%20and%20has%20found%20solutions%20of%20some%20of%20them%20which%20well%20deserve%20the%20attention%20even%20of%20those%20who%20have%20studied%20Plato%20and%20Kant%2C%20I%20should%20point%20to%20India.%20And%20if%20I%20were%20to%20ask%20myself%20from%20what%20literature%20we%20who%20have%20been%20nurtured%20almost%20exclusively%20on%20the%20thoughts%20of%20Greeks%20and%20Romans%2C%20and%20of%20the%20Semitic%C2%A0%20race%2C%20the%20Jewish%2C%20may%20draw%20the%20corrective%20which%20is%20most%20wanted%20in%20order%20to%20make%20our%20inner%20life%20more%20established%20after%20the%20European%20pattern%20were%20too%20expensive%20for%20the%20people%2C%20and%20therefore%20they%20could%20not%20possibly%20overtake%20the%20thing.%20I%20defy%20anybody%20to%20fulfil%20a%20programme%20of%20compulsory%20primary%20education%20of%20these%20masses%20inside%20of%20a%20century.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20century%20after%20the%20Mahatma%E2%80%99s%20uncharacteristically%20passionate%20outburst%2C%20if%20we%20are%20to%20take%20a%20relatively%20more%20objective%20view%20of%20the%20colonial%20impact%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20knowledge%20traditions%2C%20two%20significant%20elements%20deserve%20attention.%20The%20first%20of%20these%20is%20that%20the%20pervasive%20cultural%20amnesia%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20intellectual%20failures%20and%20accomplishments%20seems%20to%20have%20hampered%20our%20ability%20to%20establish%20organic%20links%20between%20the%20past%20and%20the%20present.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20last%20two%20centuries%2C%20Indians%20have%20either%20entirely%20dismissed%20all%20that%20we%20had%20cultivated%20as%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20in%20theory%20as%20well%20as%20a%20million%20everyday%20tasks.%20Or%20else%2C%20we%20tend%20to%20think%20that%20ancient%20India%20had%20all-encompassing%20knowledge%20in%20all%20domains%20and%20tend%20to%20glorify%20that%20imagined%20past.%20But%20unquestioning%20adulation%20or%20complete%20dismissal%20is%20no%20substitute%20for%20a%20critical%20perspective.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F08%2F421073631_1459759ec3_b.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20lecture%20hall%20at%20IIT-Kharagpur.%20Credit%3A%20ambuj%2FFlickr%2C%20CC%20BY%202.0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F08%2F421073631_1459759ec3_b.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F08%2F421073631_1459759ec3_b-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-8858%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98T%3Cspan%3Ehe%20intensity%20with%20which%20Indian%20scholars%20have%20felt%20this%20discriminating%20attitude%20has%20been%20acute.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Photo%3A%20ambuj%2FFlickr%2C%20CC%20BY%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20element%20was%20the%20frequently%20noticed%20%E2%80%98time%20lag%E2%80%99%20between%20the%20knowledge%20in%20the%20West%20and%20that%20in%20India%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20parity%20between%20knowledge%20production%20in%20the%20global%20West%20and%20the%20global%20South.%20Countries%20such%20as%20Ireland%2C%20Canada%20and%20Australia%20too%20had%20to%20fight%20Western%20disapproval%20of%20knowledge%20coming%20from%20former%20colonies.%20But%20the%20intensity%20with%20which%20Indian%20scholars%20have%20felt%20this%20discriminating%20attitude%20has%20generally%20been%20more%20acute.%20It%20would%20be%20fair%20to%20add%20that%20the%20colonised%20African%20countries%20have%20had%20an%20even%20greater%20difficulty%20in%20having%20their%20forms%20of%20knowledge%20acknowledged%20as%20%E2%80%98universal%E2%80%99%20knowledge.%20The%20African%20reactions%20too%20have%20been%20far%20more%20pointed.%20As%20a%20result%20a%20whole%20cultural%20movement%20called%20%E2%80%98Negritude%E2%80%99%20sprang%20up%20in%20reaction%20in%20many%20African%20countries.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENgugi%20Wa%20Thiong%E2%80%99o%2C%20the%20most%20eloquent%20of%20the%20spokespersons%20for%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20selfhood%2C%20wrote%20in%20his%20memorable%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMoving%20the%20Centre%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Struggle%20for%20Cultural%20Freedoms%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20suspicious%20of%20the%20uses%20of%20the%20word%20(the%20Third%20World)%20and%20the%20concept%20of%20the%20universal.%20For%20very%20often%2C%20this%20has%20meant%20the%20West%20generalising%20its%20experience%20of%20history%20as%20the%20universal%20experience%20of%20the%20world.%20What%20is%20Western%20becomes%20universal%20and%20what%20is%20Third%20World%20becomes%20local%E2%80%A6%20The%20Eurocentric%20basis%20of%20seeing%20the%20world%20has%20often%20meant%20marginalising%20into%20the%20periphery%20that%20which%20comes%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20colonial%20disruption%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20self-perception%20and%20the%20uneven%20cultural%20relationship%20emerging%20out%20of%20the%20context%20of%20the%20West%E2%80%99s%20intellectual%20domination%20of%20the%20colonised%20people%20continued%20to%20prevail%20well%20beyond%20the%20formal%20end%20of%20colonial%20rule.%20The%20intellectual%20biography%20of%20D.%20D.%20Kosambi%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20more%20original%20thinkers%20in%20the%20post-Independence%20decades%2C%20brings%20home%20poignantly%20the%20cultural%20asymmetry%20in%20the%20field%20of%20%E2%80%98universal%E2%80%99%20sciences.%20Reflecting%20on%20the%20response%20to%20his%20fundamental%20contribution%20to%20number%20theory%20in%20mathematics%2C%20Kosambi%20observes%20that%20an%20Indian%20contribution%20to%20a%20theoretical%20field%20of%20knowledge%20usually%20met%20with%20suspicion%20and%20disregard.%20When%20Kosambi%20proposed%20that%20the%20Poisson%20distribution%20would%20explain%20the%20prime%20number%20theory%2C%20he%20had%20to%20spend%20several%20years%20to%20get%20a%20sympathetic%20audience%20among%20Western%20mathematicians.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20comments%20in%20despair%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20competent%20judge%20who%20saw%20only%20this%20radically%20new%20basic%20result%20intuitively%20felt%20that%20it%20was%20correct%20as%20well%20as%20of%20fundamental%20importance.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20Riemann%20hypothesis%20followed%20as%20a%20simple%20consequence.%20Could%20a%20problem%20over%20which%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20mathematicians%20have%20come%20to%20grief%20for%20over%20a%20century%20thus%20casually%20be%20solved%20in%20the%20jungles%20of%20India%3F%20Psychologically%2C%20it%20seemed%20much%20more%20probable%20that%20the%20interloper%20was%20just%20another%20%E2%80%98circle-squarer%E2%80%99.%20Mathematics%20may%20be%20a%20cold%2C%20impersonal%20science%20of%20pure%20thought%3B%20the%20mathematician%20can%20be%20thoughtless%2C%20heatedly%20acrid%2C%20even%20rabid%2C%20over%20what%20he%20dislikes%E2%80%A6%20I%20had%20to%20fight%20for%20my%20results%20over%20three%20long%20years%E2%80%A6%20There%20is%20surely%20a%20great%20deal%20to%20be%20said%20for%20the%20notion%20that%20the%20success%20of%20science%20is%20fundamentally%20related%20to%20the%20particular%20form%20of%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20my%20own%20work%2C%20during%20my%20formative%20years%2C%20I%20have%20often%20taken%20a%20position%20that%20would%20be%20akin%20to%20Dharampal%E2%80%99s%20painstaking%20research%2C%20showing%20how%20British%20colonial%20rule%20in%20India%20destroyed%20the%20traditions%20of%20education%20existing%20during%20the%20immediately%20preceding%20era.%20I%20have%20also%20commented%20in%20detail%20on%20the%20cultural%20amnesia%20that%20set%20in%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20colonial%20encounter.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20several%20eminent%20thinkers%20and%20educationists%20and%20various%20reports%20on%20education%20have%20pointed%20out%20the%20loss%20of%20originality%20in%20pedagogic%20practices%20and%20knowledge%20production%20in%20India%20caused%20by%20the%20imposition%20of%20a%20language%20that%20is%20not%20one%E2%80%99s%20mother%20tongue%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20higher%20order%20cognitive%20transactions.%20However%2C%20though%20the%20colonial%20experience%20can%20be%20justifiably%20held%20responsible%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20disproportionately%20low%20contribution%20to%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20during%20the%20last%20two%20centuries%2C%20focusing%20on%20colonialism%20alone%20may%20not%20yield%20the%20complete%20story%20of%20our%20failure.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20possible%20to%20counterpoise%20Dharampal%E2%80%99s%20research%20with%20another%20significant%20work%20of%20research%2C%20one%20that%20has%20had%20equally%20enormous%20impact%2C%20but%20quite%20differently%2C%20on%20our%20self%20perception.%20That%20work%20is%20the%20text%20of%20a%20lecture%20that%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%20was%20to%20deliver%20at%20Lahore%20%E2%80%93%20but%20could%20not%20%E2%80%93%20and%20was%20published%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20book%20titled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAnnihilation%20of%20Caste%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%201936.%20Ambedkar%20presents%20in%20this%20work%20a%20scathing%20analysis%20of%20the%20social%20inequalities%20prevailing%20in%20India%20for%20over%20two%20millennia%20and%20a%20passionate%20plea%20for%20genuine%20equality.%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20was%20probably%20the%20most%20educated%20of%20the%20Indian%20leaders%20of%20his%20time%20with%20degrees%20from%20Columbia%20University%20and%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Economics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22school%20education%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-649250%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98To%20educate%E2%80%99%20the%20deprived%20classes%20to%20create%20an%20equitable%20society%20was%20one%20of%20his%20non-negotiable%20articles%20of%20faith.%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20analysis%20opens%20up%20the%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20question%20in%20India%2C%20taking%20it%20beyond%20the%20easily%20available%20proof%20of%20the%20culpability%20of%20colonial%C2%A0%20domination%2C%20and%20takes%20it%20back%20to%20the%20ancient%20times%20when%20various%20theological%20schools%20inscribed%20discrimination%20as%20a%20social%20norm%20in%20India.%20My%20purpose%20is%C2%A0%20not%20to%20judge%20Gandhi%20or%20Ambedkar.%20It%20is%20common%20among%20Indian%20intellectuals%20to%20position%20Gandhi%20and%20Ambedkar%20as%20intellectual%20adversaries%20and%20take%20umbrage%20on%20behalf%20of%20one%20or%20the%20other.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20aim%20is%20not%20to%20assess%20either%20Ambedkar%20or%20Gandhi%20and%20their%20views%20on%20knowledge%20or%20education%3B%20the%20aim%20here%20is%20to%20look%20at%20the%20question%20of%20knowledge%20and%20its%20formally%20institutionalised%20means%2C%20education.%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20caste%20discrimination%20in%20the%20past%20and%20in%20the%20present%2C%20the%20colonial%20cultural%20domination%20and%20the%20continued%20%E2%80%98knowledge%20imperialism%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20West%2C%20have%20had%20an%20effect%20in%20reducing%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20in%20India%20to%20pauperisation%20and%20%E2%80%98education%E2%80%99%20in%20India%20to%20a%20savage%20mockery%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20education.%20To%20take%20both%20these%20givens%20into%20account%20should%20benefit%20any%20analysis%20of%20the%C2%A0%20condition%20of%20education%20in%20contemporary%20India.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20as%20the%20650%20million%20Indians%20born%20after%201990%20look%20up%20to%20moving%20forward%20into%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20with%20education%20as%20their%20most%20desired%20means%20for%20that%20movement%20and%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20as%20the%20driving%20engine%20for%20their%20very%20survival%2C%20it%20may%20be%20beneficial%20if%20an%20analysis%20of%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20can%20be%20carried%20out%20from%20%E2%80%98within%E2%80%99%2C%20by%20looking%20at%20itself%20without%20unduly%20shifting%20the%20focus%20to%20the%20impact%20of%20colonialism%20or%20the%20legacy%20of%20caste%20hegemony.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20I%20do%20not%20intend%20in%20the%20least%20to%20deny%20the%20primacy%20of%20these%20factors%20in%20any%20analysis%20of%20the%20condition%20of%20education%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EG.N.%20Devy%20is%20a%20former%20professor%20and%20cultural%20activist%2C%20best%20known%20for%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3EPeople%E2%80%99s%20Linguistic%20Survey%20of%20India%3Cem%3E%20and%20the%20Adivasi%20Academy%20created%20by%20him.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707043824000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F21135412%2FIMG_2345.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fgn-devy-iit-bombay-cancelled-lecture%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Though%20the%20colonial%20experience%20can%20be%20justifiably%20held%20responsible%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20disproportionately%20low%20contri