itle%22%3A%22There%E2%80%99s%20Temple%20Politics%20Where%20You%20Least%20Expect%20It%20%E2%80%93%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Jungle%20Mahal%2C%20for%20One%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04150323%2FChapter-5-photograph-2.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20January%2023%2C%202017%20%E2%80%93%20nearly%20three%20years%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20would%20give%20the%20historic%20verdict%20on%20Ram%20temple%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Gangajalghati%20subdivision%20of%20Bankura%2C%20an%20old%20autorickshaw%20passed%20through%20the%20dusty%20village%20road.%20It%20was%20being%20chased%20by%20Santhali%20kids%20from%20Shiulibona%20village%20and%20as%20it%20sped%20up%2C%20I%20heard%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20grand%20inauguration%20of%20a%20Hanuman%20temple%20near%20Jamshala%20village%20the%20next%20day.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKids%20were%20excited%2C%20so%20was%20my%20key%20informant%20from%20Jamshala%20Shyamal%20Mandi%2C%20about%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%20in%20their%20village%20instead%20of%20Shiulibona.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20I%20met%20Rabon%20Shoren%2C%20a%20middle-aged%20tribal%20gentleman%2C%20who%20introduced%20me%20to%20%E2%80%98Samayita%20Math%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20quasi-religious%20Hindu%20centre%20in%20Shiulibona.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESamayita%20Math%20runs%20an%20open%20prayer%20hall%20and%20has%20installed%20a%20road-side%20temple-like%20structure%20in%20the%20village%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Marang%20Buru.%20Approximately%20one%20kilometre%20from%20the%20Susunia%20hills%20is%20the%20Santhali%20Disham%20shrine%20%E2%80%93%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20religio-political%20hierarchy%20of%20the%20Santhal%20tradition.%20The%20shrine%20has%20three%20erected%20stones%20and%2C%20now%20aided%20with%20a%20submersible%20pump%20set%2C%20an%20overhead%20tank%20for%20the%20visitors%20to%20have%20access%20to%20basic%20amenities.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20are%20recent%20developments%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rabon%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%2015%2C%202020%2C%20while%20driving%20from%20Purulia%20towards%20Ranchi%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20stay%20at%20the%20Pathersathi%20hotel%20in%20Chashmore%2C%20developed%20by%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20and%20run%20by%20local%20self%20help%20groups.%20It%20was%20easy%20to%20get%20rooms%20as%20not%20many%20were%20travelling%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20On%20my%20way%2C%20I%20encountered%20a%20Hanuman%20temple%20at%20each%20village%20we%20crossed.%20My%20travel%20partner%20Sukumar%20Hansda%2C%20a%20local%20young%20guy%2C%20saw%20my%20curiosity%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20they%20kept%20a%20Hanuman%20idol%2C%20then%20they%20constructed%20a%20plinth%20and%20then%20a%20temple.%E2%80%9D%20On%20being%20asked%20who%20%E2%80%98they%E2%80%99%20were%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHindus%E2%80%A6%20they%20are%20many.%20Bajrang%20dal%2C%20Durgashakti%2C%20Vanvasi%20Kalyan%20Ashram..%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhunger-and-broken-promises-in-jungle-mahal%5C%22%3EOnce%20a%20Maoist%20Hotbed%2C%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Jungle%20Mahal%20Is%20Now%20Battling%20Hunger%20and%20Anger%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20realised%20that%20the%20hotel%20where%20we%20were%20staying%20was%20located%20exactly%20between%20two%20such%20temples%20%E2%80%93%20one%20at%20Dumardih%20Upar%20Para%20and%20another%20one%20at%20Velaidihi.%20There%20was%20another%20a%20little%20inside%20the%20village%20at%20Tanasi.%20All%20three%20were%20constructed%20almost%20overnight%20in%202019%2C%20a%20few%20months%20before%20the%20parliamentary%20elections.%20Before%20that%20they%20were%20open%20installations%20of%20Hanuman%20idols.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20three%20villages%20have%20mixed%20population%2C%20predominated%20by%20Hindus%2C%20a%20few%20hamlets%20of%20Santhal%20people%20and%20a%20small%20ghettoised%20Muslim%20settlement%20on%20the%20northern%20side.%20The%20three%20temples%20ran%20%3Cem%3EHanuman%20Chalisa%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20a%20loudspeaker%20that%20were%20directed%20towards%20the%20Muslim%20settlement.%20Visibly%20afraid%2C%20none%20of%20the%20Muslims%2C%20during%20my%20first%20visit%2C%20said%20anything%20about%20the%20temple.%20They%20maintained%20that%20such%20constructions%20or%20the%20loudspeaker%2C%20which%20was%20quite%20noisy%20even%20to%20my%20urban%20ear%20habituated%20with%20everyday%20cacophony%2C%20did%20not%20affect%20their%20everyday%20life.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20my%20subsequent%20visits%20to%20the%20villages%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20all%20three%20temples%20were%20constructed%20by%20taking%20subscription%20money%20from%20the%20villagers%20which%20included%20both%20Hindus%20and%20Santhals.%20People%20belonging%20to%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%20from%20Joypur%20appointed%20village%20level%20volunteers%20for%20temple%20construction%20and%20now%20they%20are%20run%20by%20temple%20committees.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvenings%20are%20well%20spent%20near%20the%20temple%20site%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Emahant%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chief%20priest)%20worships%20Ram%20and%20Hanuman%2C%20narrating%20stories%20of%20the%20great%20power.%20Villagers%20are%20also%20told%20that%20in%20a%20remote%20past%2C%20they%20protected%20local%20kings%20and%20their%20beautiful%20daughters%20from%20getting%20abducted%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98ruthless%20Muslim%20rulers%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EBackground%20of%20Jungle%20Mahal%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBetween%202008-2011%2C%20Jungle%20Mahal%20(Bankura%2C%20Purulia%20and%20West%20Midnapore%20and%20Jhargram%20districts%20of%20West%20Bengal)%20had%20seen%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.satp.org%2Fdatasheet-terrorist-attack%2Ffatalities%2Findia-maoistinsurgency-westbengal%5C%22%3Ebloodiest%20episodes%20of%20violence%20in%20independent%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20total%20of%20505%20civilians%20getting%20killed%20during%20the%20period%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBased%20on%20a%20longitudinal%2C%20mixed%20method%20study%20in%20a%20recently%20published%20journal%20article%20we%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Farticle%2F10.1007%2Fs12116-023-09389-w%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20while%20the%20rebel%20align%20party%20wins%20immediately%20after%20the%20civil%20war%2C%20their%20continuation%20depends%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20violence%20used%20by%20the%20rebel%20groups.%20In%20case%20of%20Jungle%20Mahal.%20the%20sudden%20disappearance%20of%20Maoist%20rebels%2C%20especially%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2FKishenji-killed-in-encounter%2Farticle13499991.ece%5C%22%3Ethe%20death%20of%20Kishen%20ji%20%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20their%20counterparts%2C%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20or%20CPI(M)-controlled%20Harmad%20Bahini%2C%20led%20to%20an%20organisational%20vacuum.%20Such%20vacuum%20was%20never%20compensated%20and%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20government%20did%20what%20is%20termed%20as%20hyper-development%20using%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F14672715.2017.1415762%5C%22%3E%20non-elected%20arms%20of%20the%20local%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-rss-hindutva-bengal-nationalist-icons%5C%22%3EBJP%20and%20the%20Art%20of%20Selling%20Hindutva%20Nationalism%20to%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20precisely%20in%20this%20moment%20of%20absence%20of%20organisations%20that%20Jungle%20Mahal%20saw%20a%20proliferation%20of%20Hanuman%20idols%20and%20temples.%20Coordinated%20precisely%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F886576%2Fground-report-how-the-bjp-is-gaining-in-west-bengals-one-time-maoist-stronghold-jungle-mahal%5C%22%3EEkal%20Vidyalayas%20and%20Vanvasi%20Kalyan%20Ashram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Ram%20Navami%20processions%20soon%20ventured%20on%20the%20newly%20constructed%20roads%20laid%20by%20the%20TMC.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20everyday%20image%20of%20Hindutva%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETemple%20politics%20at%20the%20grassroots%20has%20been%20rather%20successful%20in%20translating%20popular%20support%20to%20gain%20electoral%20dividend%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20The%20four%20major%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20of%20Jungle%20Mahal%20were%20won%20by%20the%20BJP%20with%20astonishing%20increase%20in%20electoral%20support%20base.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20increased%20by%2014.4%25%20in%20Bankura%2C%20Purulia%20(42.1%25)%2C%20Bishnupur%20(32.1%25)%20and%20Jhargram%20(34.8%25)%20as%20compared%20to%202014.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20it%20would%20be%20immature%20to%20associate%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20win%20solely%20to%20temple%20politics.%20There%20are%20reasons%20related%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F886576%2Fground-report-how-the-bjp-is-gaining-in-west-bengals-one-time-maoist-stronghold-jungle-mahal%5C%22%3ETMC%E2%80%99s%20failures%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20However%2C%20temple%20politics%20does%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20uniting%20an%20otherwise%20diverse%20pool%20of%20voters%20against%20a%20common%20enemy%2C%20the%20Muslims%2C%20for%20a%20common%20cause%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98search%20for%20the%20true%20soul%20of%20Bharat%E2%80%99%20and%20for%20a%20common%20insecurity%20that%20%E2%80%98Hindus%20are%20in%20danger%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.routledge.com%2FDemocracy-and-Social-Cleavage-in-India-Ethnography-of-Riots-Everyday-Politics%2FNath%2Fp%2Fbook%2F9781032226453%5C%22%3Eongoing%20ethnographic%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20find%20out%20people%E2%80%99s%20engagement%20in%20Hindutva%20ideology%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20If%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faamrabharatbarsha.com%2Fwelcome%2Fcategory%2FConflict%2520%26amp%3B%2520Co-existence%2520Reports%5C%22%3Eeveryday%20polarisation%20through%20low-intense%20riots%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20resulted%20in%20wide%20spread%20of%20fundamentalist%20sentiments%20among%20both%20the%20communities%20is%20one%20of%20the%20mechanisms%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ijcv.org%2Findex.php%2Fijcv%2Farticle%2Fview%2F3119%5C%22%3Einvented%20traditions%20is%20another%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20parallel%20to%20this%20has%20been%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20image%20among%20the%20villagers%20of%20the%20remote%20villages%20of%20Jungle%20Mahal.%20Before%20the%20invention%20of%20Ram%20Navami%20processions%2C%20which%20frequently%20results%20in%20riots%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0these%20temples%20served%20as%20the%20primary%20%E2%80%98logo%E2%80%99%20and%20entry%20point%20to%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbengal-ram-navami-bihar-violence%5C%22%3E%20grand%20Hindutva%20model%20in%20West%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20287px)%2085vw%2C%20287px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04150535%2FConclusions-photograph-1-768x1024.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22287%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04150535%2FConclusions-photograph-1-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04150535%2FConclusions-photograph-1-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04150535%2FConclusions-photograph-1.jpg%20900w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695661%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22383%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20shrine%20in%20Kolkata%20where%20a%20Hanuman%20idol%20can%20be%20seen.%20Photo%3A%20Author%20provided%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20while%20every%20village%20of%20Jungle%20Mahal%20region%20has%20a%20Hanuman%20temple%2C%20bright%20orange%20flags%20and%20relatively%20smaller%20Hanuman%20idols%20are%20kept%20in%20the%20pre-existing%20shrines%20of%20Shitala%20and%20Manasha%20cult%20which%20has%20been%20worshipped%20by%20the%20villagers%20since%20time%20immemorial.%20Spatial%20and%20boundary%20principles%20are%20attached%20to%20the%20traditional%20shrines%20and%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshodhganga.inflibnet.ac.in%2Fhandle%2F10603%2F18159%5C%22%3E%20their%20archaeological%20continuity%20and%20significance%20is%20enormous%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENeedless%20to%20say%2C%20these%20have%20created%20a%20special%20space%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20the%20people%20who%20worship%20them.%20It%20was%20the%20everyday%20form%20of%20benevolent%20local%20goddess%20who%20were%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20protectors%20of%20people%20from%20snakebites%20and%20infectious%20diseases.%20They%20were%20never%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20ideology.%20These%20goddesses%20are%20usually%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.2307%2F1177724%5C%22%3Eworshipped%20by%20the%20women%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20these%20villages%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20men%20placing%20a%20Hanuman%20idol%20next%20to%20them%20is%20not%20only%20an%20intrusion%20of%20masculinity%20within%20the%20feminine%20sphere%2C%20but%20also%20an%20introduction%20of%20the%20masculine%20Hindutva%20thought%20in%20the%20folk%20tradition%20of%20village%20deities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20several%20villages%2C%20where%20Hanuman%20idols%20are%20placed%20in%20existing%20sacred%20groves%2C%20villagers%2C%20including%20the%20women%20haven%E2%80%99t%20found%20it%20unusual.%20Hanuman%E2%80%99s%20stories%20are%20being%20narrated%20through%20oral%20traditions%20and%20in%20school-level%20texts.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20harm%20in%20having%20Pavanputra%20in%20the%20village%2C%20he%20is%20a%20Hindu%20%3Cem%3Edevta%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20we%20should%20worship%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20women%20from%20Gangajalghati%20said%20during%20a%20casual%20conversation%20among%20the%20villagers%20during%20my%20visit%20last%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20ideology%20of%20Hindutva%20is%20expanding%20its%20base%20among%20the%20poor%20and%20marginalised%20because%20of%20the%20narrative%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20RSS%20has%20been%20so%20successful%20in%20building.%20We%20know%20that%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20not%20where%20they%20would%20stop%2C%20perhaps%20it%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20their%20plan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20And%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20temple%20politics%20in%20Jungle%20Mahal%2C%20which%20has%20helped%20BJP%20in%20bagging%20several%20constituencies%2C%20is%20just%20one%20small%20part%20of%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20groves%20and%20temples%20that%20were%20decked%20with%20bright%20orange%20flags%20of%20angry%20hanuman%20and%20Ram%20images%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20January%2022%20have%20further%20made%20an%20impact%20into%20the%20cultural-cognitive%20dimensions%20of%20these%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESuman%20Nath%20teaches%20anthropology%20at%20Dr.%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%20Government%20College%20and%20is%20the%20author%20of%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EDemocracy%20and%20Social%20Cleavage%20in%20India%20Ethnography%20of%20Riots%2C%20Everyday%20Politics%20and%20Communalism%20in%20West%20Bengal%20c.%202012%E2%80%932021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707040845000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04150323%2FChapter-5-photograph-2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftheres-temple-politics-where-you-least-expect-it-bengals-jungle-mahal-for-one%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Before%20the%20invention%20of%20Ram%20Navami%20processions%2C%20which%20frequently%20results%20in%20riots%2C%C2%A0these%20temples%20served%20as%20the%20primary%20'logo'%20and%20entry%20point%20to%20the%20grand%20Hindutva%20model%20in%20West%20Bengal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftheres-temple-politics-where-you-least-expect-it-bengals-jungle-mahal-for-one%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Did%20Puja%20at%20Gyanvapi'%3A%20Now%2C%20BJP's%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%2C%20Uma%20Bharti%20Back%20Hindu%20Plaintiffs'%20Claim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04152216%2FUntitled-design-8.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Aligning%20with%20the%20claims%20of%20the%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20matter%20and%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%2C%20at%20least%20two%20senior%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leaders%20have%20publicly%20claimed%20that%20they%20had%20performed%20puja%20facing%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20mosque%20or%20in%20its%20basement%20before%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Varanasi%20administration%2C%20executing%20the%20controversial%20orders%20of%20a%20district%20court%2C%20supervised%20the%20installation%20of%20idols%20of%20Hindu%20deities%20inside%20the%20southern%20cellar%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20arranged%20prayer%20rituals%20by%20a%20Hindu%20priest%20there.%20The%20administration%20has%20also%20cut%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20steel%20barricade%20that%20secures%20the%20mosque%20to%20allow%20the%20entry%20of%20the%20Hindu%20priests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caretakers%20of%20the%20mosque%20have%20described%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfalse%20and%20baseless%E2%80%9D%20the%20claims%20by%20a%20Hindu%20plaintiff%20that%20idols%20of%20Hindu%20deities%20existed%20inside%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20that%20they%20used%20to%20be%20worshipped%20by%20his%20ancestors%20till%20the%20mosque%20was%20barricaded%20in%20December%201993%20following%20Supreme%20Court%20orders%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKeshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20February%203%2C%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20claimed%20that%20till%201993%2C%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20%E2%80%9CVyas%20ji%20ka%20tehkhana%E2%80%9D%20was%20open%20and%20people%20would%20offer%20prayers%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20had%20the%20good%20fortune%20of%20doing%20%E2%80%98darshan%E2%80%99%20there.%20But%20in%201993%20it%20was%20stopped%2C%E2%80%9D%20Maurya%20said%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9CShri%20Ram%20Darbar%E2%80%9D%2C%20an%20event%20organised%20by%20a%20newly-launched%20right-wing%20platform%20Shri%20Guru%20Vasishtha%20Nyas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaurya%2C%20who%20described%20the%20puja%20inside%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%E2%80%9D%20event%2C%20also%20said%20that%20if%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20of%20which%20he%20was%20a%20part%2C%20wanted%20it%20could%20have%20opened%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%20for%20Hindu%20prayers%20but%20it%20chose%20to%20not%20intervene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leaders%20as%20well%20as%20members%20of%20Hindutva%20groups%20have%20claimed%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Edarshan%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20Hindu%20deities%20near%20the%20wall%20of%20the%20mosque%20was%20stopped%20during%20the%20rule%20of%20then%20chief%20minister%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20in%201993.%20The%20saffron%20party%20has%20for%20years%20tried%20to%20appease%20Hindu%20voters%20by%20referring%20to%20the%20firing%20on%20%3Cem%3Ekar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Esevaks%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%201990%20when%20they%20were%20attempting%20to%20demolish%20the%20Babri%20Masjid.%20With%20a%20court%20in%20Varanasi%20handing%20over%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20to%20Hindus%20for%20puja%2C%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20now%20actively%20trying%20to%20drag%20the%20main%20opposition%20Samajwadi%20Party%20into%20the%20controversy%20as%20it%20tries%20to%20further%20polarise%20Hindu%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20double%20engine%20government%20working%20in%20the%20country%20and%20the%20state%20with%20impartiality.%20What%20happened%20during%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20government%20in%201993%2C%20we%20could%20have%20%5Baltered%20it%5D%20after%20we%20formed%20the%20government%20in%202017%20but%20we%20did%20not%20do%20any%20such%20thing.%20The%20shiv%20bhakts%20and%20plaintiffs%20took%20the%20shelter%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Maurya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpuja-to-continue-in-gyanvapi-basement-no-hc-relief-feb-6%5C%22%3ENo%20Immediate%20HC%20Relief%2C%20Puja%20to%20Continue%20Inside%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20Basement%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUma%20Bharti%20and%20Alok%20Kumar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20Maurya%2C%20on%20January%2031%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20district%20court%20order%2C%20former%20union%20minister%20Uma%20Bharti%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20the%20most%20recognisable%20women%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20of%20the%20early%201990s%20%E2%80%93%20also%20claimed%20that%20she%20had%20worshipped%20the%20%E2%80%9Cidols%20inscribed%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Varanasi%20district%20court%20decision%20on%20Gyanvapi%20is%20pleasant.%20I%20have%20myself%20worshipped%20the%20idols%20inscribed%20on%20the%20walls%20of%20Gyanvapi%20in%201993%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bharti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20sought%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfinal%20solution%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20dispute%20and%20said%20that%20the%20land%20on%20which%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20in%20Varanasi%20and%20the%20Shahi%20Eidgah%20Masjid%20in%20Mathura%20stand%2C%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20Hindus%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20temples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20VHP%20too%20has%20made%20a%20similar%20claim%20in%20public%20declaring%20the%20southern%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctemple.%E2%80%9D%20The%20far-right%20organization%20affiliated%20to%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20said%20that%20till%201993%2C%20%E2%80%9Cregular%20puja%20archana%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20deities%20was%20going%20on%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%201993%2C%20the%20administration%20had%2C%20in%20an%20arbitrary%20action%2C%20barricaded%20the%20area%2C%20prohibited%20the%20Hindus%20from%20going%20to%20the%20temple%20and%20stopped%20the%20puja%20archana%2C%E2%80%9D%20VHP%20international%20working%20president%20Alok%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fjudge-hands-over-gyanvapi-basement-to-hindus%5C%22%3EA%20Day%20Before%20Retiring%2C%20Varanasi%20Judge%20Hands%20Over%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20Basement%20to%20Hindus%20For%20Worship%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20role%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20suit%20filed%20in%202022%2C%20Rakhi%20Singh%20and%20four%20other%20Hindu%20women%2C%20made%20a%20similar%20claim%20that%20the%20devotees%20of%20Lord%20Shiva%20were%20performing%20daily%20puja%20and%20worship%20of%20Maa%20Shringar%20Gauri%20and%20other%20visible%20and%20invisible%20deities%20within%20the%20%E2%80%9Cold%20temple%E2%80%9D%20continuously%20till%201990%20when%20the%20state%20government%20in%20view%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20movement%20put%20restrictions%20on%20the%20daily%20puja.%20Since%201993%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20under%20the%20oral%20orders%20of%20the%20state%20government%20allowed%20devotees%20to%20perform%20puja%20only%20once%20a%20year%2C%20on%20the%204th%20day%20of%20Vasantik%20Navratra%20in%20Chaitra%2C%20Rakhi%20Singh%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20opposition%20in%20UP%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20has%20so%20far%20not%20openly%20rebutted%20the%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20VHP%20and%20the%20Hindu%20plaintiffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20district%20administration%20started%20puja%20inside%20the%20basement%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20February%201%2C%20SP%20president%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20criticized%20the%20developments%2C%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwhat%20we%3Cbr%3E%5Cnare%20seeing%20now%20is%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20go%20beyond%20the%20due%20process%20and%20prevent%20any%20legal%20recourse%20that%20can%20be%20taken.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%2C%20while%20stressing%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20district%20court%20had%20asked%20the%20administration%20to%20comply%20with%20its%20order%20in%20seven%20days%2C%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20process%20had%20to%20be%20maintained%20while%20following%20any%20court%20order.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Ram%20Gopal%20Yadav%20was%20asked%20by%20journalists%20outside%20Parliament%20on%20February%202%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20claims%20that%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20had%20stopped%20puja%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Mosque%20during%20his%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20visibly%20irritated%20Ram%20Gopal%20Yadav%20responded%2C%20%E2%80%9CWho%20is%20saying%20Mulayam%20Singh%20stopped%20prayers%3F%20Only%20idiots%20can%20say%20like%20this%20(%3Cem%3Esic%3C%2Fem%3E).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20argued%20that%20court%20decisions%20were%20not%20always%20correct%20or%20absolute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNothing%20is%20absolutely%20correct.%20Nothing%20is%20absolutely%20perfect.%20Every%20decision%2C%20for%20one%20side%20it%20is%20right%2C%20for%20another%20side%20it%20is%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Funderstanding-the-gyanvapi-mosque-dispute-what-does-the-places-of-worship-act-say%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20Case%3A%20What%20Does%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%20Say%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98There%20is%20no%20limit%20to%20their%20lying%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Anjuman%20Intezamia%20Masajid%20Comittee%20Varanasi%2C%20which%20manages%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%2C%20in%20a%20new%20statement%20condemned%20the%20action%20by%20the%20court%20and%20administration%20as%20%E2%80%9Cone-sided.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20assure%20you%20that%20we%20will%20fight%20for%20the%20protection%20and%20security%20of%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20Gyanvapi%20till%20our%20last%20breath%2C%E2%80%9D%20Maulana%20Abdul%20Batin%20Nomani%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Anjuman%20Intezamia%20Committee%2C%20said%20in%20a%20note%20addressed%20to%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Masjid%20committee%20has%20maintained%2C%20inside%20and%20outside%20court%2C%20that%20question%20of%20stopping%20Hindus%20from%20conducting%20puja%20from%20December%201993%20did%20not%20arise%20as%20no%20member%20of%20the%20Vyas%20family%20ever%20carried%20out%20puja%20in%20the%20cellar.%20No%20idol%20was%20ever%20present%20inside%20the%20basement%2C%20the%20committee%20said%2C%20stressing%20that%20it%20had%20always%20been%20under%20their%20occupation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES.%20M.%20Yasin%2C%20joint%20secretary%20of%20the%20Anjuman%20Intezamia%20Masajid%2C%20dismissed%20the%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20that%20they%20had%20offered%20prayers%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%20or%20facing%20its%20walls%20till%20at%20least%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20lies.%20There%20is%20no%20limit%20to%20their%20lying.%20No%20such%20puja%20has%20ever%20happened.%20The%20plaintiff%20did%20not%20provide%20any%20evidence%20in%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yasin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201996%2C%20some%20people%20did%20try%20to%20offer%20puja%20to%20%E2%80%9CMaa%20Shringar%20Gauri%E2%80%9D%20but%20they%20were%20chased%20away%20by%20the%20administration%2C%20said%20he.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYasin%20also%20questioned%20the%20district%20administration%E2%80%99s%20act%20of%20installing%20new%20idols%20inside%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20when%20the%20district%20court%20had%20on%20January%2031%20only%20directed%20the%20administration%20to%20conduct%20the%20puja%20and%20%E2%80%9Crag-bhog%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cidols%E2%80%9D%20inside%20the%20tehkhana%20through%20a%20pujari%20appointed%20by%20the%20Shri%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Temple%20Trust%2C%20which%20manages%20the%20adjoining%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Mandir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20order%20to%20go%20and%20keep%20new%20idols%20there%20when%20the%20plaintiff%20had%20already%20claimed%20that%20there%20were%20idols%20present%20inside.%20How%20come%20the%20ASI%20did%20not%20find%20the%20idols%20during%20its%20survey%2C%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Yasin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20compared%20the%20situation%20to%20the%20surreptitious%20planting%20of%20idols%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20inside%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%201949%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20then%20district%20magistrate%20K.K%20Nair%20who%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20Bharatiya%20Jan%20Sangh%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20both%20cases%2C%20the%20idols%20were%20planted%20surreptitiously%20in%20the%20night.%20In%201949%2C%20the%20administration%20facilitated%20it.%20In%202024%2C%20the%20administration%20themselves%20carried%20out%20the%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Yasin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fkashi-mathura-baaki-hain-why-the-ayodhya-verdict-wont-offer-any-respite-from-saffron-hatred%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Kashi-Mathura%20Baaqi%20Hain%E2%80%99%3A%20Why%20the%20Ayodhya%20Verdict%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Offer%20Any%20Respite%20From%20Saffron%20Hatred%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBall%20in%20court%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindu%20prayers%20inside%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20will%20continue%20at%20least%20till%20February%206%20as%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20on%20Friday%20did%20not%20grant%20any%20relief%20to%20the%20caretakers%20of%20the%20mosque%20seeking%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20district%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20of%20handing%20over%20the%20basement%20to%20Hindus%20for%20puja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20directed%20the%20mosque%20management%20committee%20to%20file%20a%20fresh%2C%20amended%20appeal%20against%20the%20district%20court%20order%20and%20said%20it%20would%20hear%20the%20matter%20on%20February%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20judge%20A.%20K%20Vishvesha%20on%20January%2031%20directed%20the%20district%20administration%20to%20make%20arrangements%20for%20puja%20and%20other%20Hindu%20activities%20inside%20the%20southern%20tehkhana%20(cellar)%20of%20the%20mosque%20within%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Varanasi%20court%20order%20came%20days%20after%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20in%20its%20survey%20report%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20claimed%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20Hindu%20temple%E2%80%9D%20existed%20there%20prior%20to%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20existing%20structure%20i.e%20the%20mosque%20and%20that%20parts%20of%20the%20temple%20were%20modified%20and%20used%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Islamic%20place%20of%20worship.%20The%20masjid%20committee%20is%20yet%20to%20submit%20a%20detailed%20objection%20to%20the%20report%20but%20has%20disagreed%20with%20the%20conclusions%20of%20the%20ASI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20passed%20the%20order%20on%20an%20application%20filed%20by%20a%20local%20priest%20Shailendra%20Kumar%20Pathak%20of%20the%20Acharya%20Ved%20Vyas%20Peeth%20temple%2C%20who%20had%20sought%20rights%20to%20worship%20the%20Maa%20Shringar%20Gauri%20and%20other%20alleged%20visible%20and%20invisible%20deities%20he%20claimed%20were%20in%20the%20cellar%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caretakers%20of%20the%20mosque%20rejected%20all%20claims%20made%20by%20Pathak%20that%20there%20were%20idols%20kept%20inside%20the%20previously-sealed%20cellar%20and%20that%20his%20ancestors%20used%20to%20carry%20out%20puja%20inside%20the%20cellar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Vishvesha%2C%20however%2C%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Hindu%20plaintiff%2C%20and%20directed%20the%20district%20administration%20to%20make%20necessary%20iron%20fencing%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20puja.%20The%20district%20magistrate%20had%20on%20January%2024%20completed%20the%20process%20of%20taking%20over%20the%20cellar%20after%20the%20court%20on%20January%2017%20directed%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20to%20keep%20the%20cellar%20secure%20and%20appointed%20him%20as%20the%20receiver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20application%2C%20Pathak%20claimed%20that%20there%20were%20idols%20kept%20in%20the%20southern%20cellar%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20that%20his%20ancestors%20as%20priests%20conducted%20worship%20of%20the%20idols%20kept%20there.%20However%2C%20Pathak%20further%20claimed%2C%20%E2%80%9CPujari%20Vyas%20ji%2C%E2%80%9D%20or%20Somnath%20Vyas%2C%20his%20maternal%20grandfather%2C%20was%20prevented%20from%20entering%20the%20barricaded%20area%20of%20the%20mosque%20after%20December%201993.%20The%20rag-bhog%20and%20sanskar%20rituals%20were%20also%20stopped%2C%20Pathak%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20ancient%20Hindu%20idols%20and%20several%20other%20religious%20items%20linked%20to%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20were%20inside%20the%20cellar.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20necessary%20to%20carry%20out%20regular%20puja%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Emurtis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(idols)%20inside%20the%20tehkhana%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707040843000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04152216%2FUntitled-design-8.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgyanvapi-masjid-keshav-prasad-maurya-uma-bharti%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'There%20is%20no%20limit%20to%20their%20lying.%20No%20such%20puja%20has%20ever%20happened%2C'%20the%20mosque%20authorities%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgyanvapi-masjid-keshav-prasad-maurya-uma-bharti%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BoM%20records%20highest%20growth%20in%20deposit%20mobilisation%20among%20PSU%20banks%20in%20Q3%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707040707000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_me