s)%20were%20first%20used%20on%20a%20large%20scale.%20Many%20then%20pointed%20out%20to%20the%20ECI%20that%20while%20the%20machines%20were%20fine%20as%20they%20were%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20major%20concern%20was%20the%20voter-machine%20interaction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBack%20then%20it%20was%20a%20challenge%20to%20get%20voters%20who%20were%20not%20tech%20savvy%20%E2%80%93%20and%20there%20are%20still%20many%20%E2%80%93%20to%20use%20the%20EVMs%20properly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20lot%20of%20water%20has%20flown%20down%20the%20Ganga%20since%20then%20and%20now%20EVMs%20are%20here%20to%20stay.%20There%20are%20however%20ever-increasing%20doubts%20about%20the%20reliability%20and%20dependability%20of%20the%20electronic%20voting%20system.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20lot%20has%20been%20written%20and%20said%20about%20this%20issue.%20Having%20followed%20that%2C%20I%20had%20decided%20quite%20some%20time%20ago%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20new%20that%20can%20be%20said%2C%20so%20I%20refrained%20from%20commenting%20on%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20I%20have%20recently%20come%20across%20a%20few%20prominent%20comments%20which%20prompt%20me%20to%20comment%20on%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEVS%20vs%20EVM%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20issue%20is%20of%20terminology%20and%20it%20is%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20simply%20using%20one%20word%20or%20expression%20in%20place%20of%20another.%20In%20this%20case%20it%20reflects%20a%20mindset.%20When%20the%20EVMs%20were%20first%20introduced%2C%20the%20most%20important%20feature%20was%20claimed%20to%20be%20that%20these%20were%20what%20was%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%9Cstand-alone%E2%80%9D%20machines%20which%20could%20not%20be%20connected%20with%20or%20contacted%20by%20any%20external%20source%20or%20device.%20And%20indeed%2C%20they%20are.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20ever%20since%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Voter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%2C%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20stand-alone%20EVM%20but%20a%20group%20of%20three%20machines%20comprising%20of%20an%20EVM%2C%20a%20VVPAT%20machine%2C%20and%20a%20Control%20Unit.%20These%20three%20machines%20thus%20constitute%20a%20system%20which%20correctly%20should%20be%20referred%20to%20as%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EElectronic%20Voting%20System%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(EVS).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20EVS%20is%20no%20longer%20stand-alone%20because%20the%20VVPAT%20machines%20have%20to%20be%20provided%20additional%20information%20by%20connecting%20these%20to%20external%20devices%20(laptops)%20which%20are%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20part%20of%20the%20EVS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFocusing%20the%20entire%20discussion%20using%20the%20term%20EVMs%20to%20actually%20refer%20to%20a%20group%20of%20three%20machines%20tends%20to%20confuse%20a%20lot%20of%20lay%20voters%20who%20still%20think%20that%20the%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machine%20is%20being%20discussed.%20The%20only%20people%20who%20possibly%20like%20this%20confusion%20are%20those%20who%20may%20benefit%20from%20it%20and%20let%20the%20status%20quo%20continue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMore%20technology%20versus%20simplicity%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20plethora%20of%20solutions%20and%20resolutions%20of%20the%20issue%20have%20been%20suggested%20over%20the%20years.%20A%20common%20feature%20of%20almost%20all%20suggested%20solutions%20is%20more%20and%20more%20dependence%20on%20technology.%20As%20a%20matter%20of%20fact%2C%20this%20piece%20has%20been%20prompted%20by%20the%20interview%20of%20a%20technical%20expert%20that%20I%20saw%20recently.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fz5Y6z29El3I%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22EVMs%20Can%20Be%20Manipulated%2C%20Not%20Hacked%2C%20But%20There's%20a%20Simple%2C%20Straightforward%2C%20Inexpensive%20Remedy%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETechnology%20focused%20solutions%20follow%20the%20general%20belief%20that%20all%20problems%20can%20be%20solved%20with%20increasing%20use%20of%20more%20sophisticated%20technology.%20This%20is%20indeed%20true%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20situations%20but%20not%20necessarily%20true%20in%20all%20situations.%20The%20situation%20of%20electronic%20voting%20in%20India%20seems%20to%20be%20one%20such.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuggested%20solution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20that%20a%20significant%2C%20if%20not%20large%2C%20proportion%20of%20voters%20in%20India%20are%20not%20fully%20literate%20and%20not%20very%20tech%20savvy%20(it%20needs%20to%20be%20pointed%20out%20that%20using%20a%20simple%20or%20%E2%80%98smart%E2%80%99%20cell%20phone%20does%20not%20make%20one%20necessarily%20tech-savvy)%2C%20I%20propose%20that%20we%20use%20the%20simplest%20technology%20possible%20for%20this%20purpose.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20proposal%20is%20outlined%20below%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20EVMs%20have%20been%20in%20use%20for%20quite%20some%20time%20and%20voters%20in%20general%20are%20familiar%20with%20their%20use%2C%20EVMs%20should%20be%20retained.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20VVPATs%20and%20Control%20Units%20should%20be%20removed%2C%20and%20replaced%20by%20a%20simple%20printer%20capable%20of%20printing%20a%20slip%20showing%20(a)%20the%20name%20and%20party%20symbol%20of%20the%20candidate%20that%20the%20voter%20voted%20for%20and%20(b)%20a%20bar%20code%20which%20enables%20machine%20counting%20of%20the%20slips.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20paper%20on%20which%20the%20above%20information%20is%20printed%20should%20be%20of%20good%20and%20durable%20quality%20capable%20of%20retaining%20the%20printed%20information%20for%20seven%20years%20(as%20opposed%20to%20the%20current%20paper%20from%20which%20the%20printed%20matter%20reportedly%20disappears%20after%20a%20rather%20short%20time).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20voter%20should%20be%20able%20to%20collect%20the%20slip%20from%20the%20printer%20directly%20(without%20any%20election%20official%20having%20to%20intervene%20or%20assist%20the%20voter%20in%20any%20way)%2C%20and%20place%20the%20slip%20directly%20in%20a%20common%20ballot%20box.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20the%20slips%20in%20the%20common%20ballot%20box%20should%20be%20machine-counted%20based%20on%20the%20bar%20code%20printed%20on%20each%20slip.%20This%20counting%20process%20using%20counting%20machines%20based%20on%20the%20bar%20code%20should%20not%20take%20many%20days%20as%20apprehended%20by%20the%20ECI%20whenever%20a%20demand%20for%20a%20hundred%20percent%20counting%20of%20VVPAT%20slips%20is%20made%2C%20and%20in%20which%20even%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20had%20to%20intervene%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20proposal%20bypasses%20all%20complications%20and%20suspicions%20that%20have%20arisen%20about%20the%20VVPATs.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20restate%20them%20here%20because%20they%20have%20been%20stated%20repeatedly.%20The%20only%20additional%20requirements%20are%20good%20quality%20paper%20and%20ink%20so%20that%20the%20printing%20lasts%20for%20seven%20years%2C%20and%20a%20barcode-based%20counting%20machine.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20proposed%20system%20will%20need%20some%20fine%20tuning%20and%20there%20are%20many%20experts%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20sure%20a%20country%20which%20has%20landed%20a%20vehicle%20on%20the%20moon%20can%20produce%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJagdeep%20S.%20Chhokar%20is%20a%20concerned%20citizen.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707039241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04150142%2FF-O786RagAAWr6B.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fevm-voting-machine-election-polls%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Focusing%20the%20entire%20discussion%20using%20the%20term%20EVMs%20to%20actually%20refer%20to%20a%20group%20of%20three%20machines%20tends%20to%20confuse%20a%20lot%20of%20lay%20voters%20who%20still%20think%20that%20the%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machine%20is%20being%20discussed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fevm-voting-machine-election-polls%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shrinking%20international%20aid%20and%20enduring%20conflict%20compound%20earthquake%20misery%20for%20Syrians%20one%20year%20on%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707038964000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107401243%2Cimgsize-1356912.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fshrinking-international-aid-and-enduring-conflict-compound-earthquake-misery-for-syrians-one-year-on%2Farticleshow%2F107400922.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107400922.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20year%20ago%2C%20Sido%20Naji%20experienced%20a%20devastating%20earthquake%20in%20Aleppo%20province%2C%20Syria.%20The%207.8%20magnitude%20earthquake%20killed%20over%2059%2C000%20people%20and%20caused%20widespread%20destruction.%20Survivors%20like%20Naji%20are%20living%20in%20dire%20conditions%2C%20with%20little%20reconstruction%20and%20no%20access%20to%20basic%20necessities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east