the%20military%20seized%20power%2C%20according%20to%20rights%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resultant%20crisis%20has%20also%20seen%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20economy%20heavily%20decline%20and%20is%20now%2010%25%20lower%20than%20it%20was%20in%202019%2C%20according%20to%20a%20reportby%20the%20World%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20life%20in%20urban%20areas%20appears%20to%20be%20somewhat%20normal%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20Myanmar%20is%20in%20disorder%2C%20according%20to%20Aung%20Thu%20Nyein%2C%20a%20political%20analyst%20from%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20so%20bad%20in%20the%20countryside%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20proper%20electricity%20and%20agricultural%20production%20is%20also%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aung%20told%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20of%20instability%20and%20difficult%20to%20predict%20what%20will%20happen%20next%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20businesses%20are%20stopping%20their%20activities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20said%20the%20number%20of%20displaced%20people%20in%20Myanmar%20since%20the%20coup%20has%20exceeded%20two%20million.%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20called%20Thursday%20for%20an%20end%20to%20violence%20in%20Myanmar%20and%20a%20return%20to%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVolker%20T%C3%BCrk%2C%20the%20UN%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%2C%20called%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20civilian%20rule%2C%20accountability%20of%20the%20military%2C%20and%20the%20release%20of%20political%20prisoners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAmid%20all%20the%20crises%20around%20the%20world%2C%20it%20is%20important%20no-one%20is%20forgotten.%20The%20people%20of%20Myanmar%20have%20been%20suffering%20for%20too%20long%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20an%20online%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20a%20peaceful%20solution%20possible%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20the%20military%20government%20extended%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20state%20of%20emergency%20again%20by%20another%20six%20months%2C%20a%20regular%20occurrence%20since%20the%20coup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20enough%20has%20been%20done%2C%20either%20politically%20or%20diplomatically%20to%20stop%20the%20war%2C%20said%20Sai%20Latt%2C%20a%20political%20analyst%20covering%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20revolutionary%20movements%20and%20region%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiplomatic%20efforts%20by%20the%20Association%20of%20Southeast%20Asian%20Nations%20(ASEAN)%20to%20resolve%20the%20conflict%20have%20proved%20ineffective%2C%20with%20little%20progress%20being%20made%20since%20the%2010-member%20bloc%20agreed%20on%20a%20five-point%20peace%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Myanmar%20signed%20up%20to%20but%20has%20failed%20to%20implement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%20told%20DW%20that%20Min%20Aung%20Hlaing%20has%20no%20will%20for%20any%20political%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20urged%20political%20parties%20to%20form%20people%E2%80%99s%20militia%20for%20community%20security%20and%20defense%20instead%20of%20asking%20them%20to%20help%20find%20political%20solutions%20%E2%80%94%20an%20indication%20that%20a%20peaceful%20political%20solution%20is%20not%20on%20his%20agenda%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CResistance%20groups%20are%20committed%20to%20continue%20the%20fighting%20until%20SAC%20is%20removed%2C%20as%20a%20result%2C%20the%20conflict%20will%20continue%20in%202024%20and%20beyond%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Sai%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Myanmar%20military%20government%2C%20which%20calls%20itself%20the%20State%20Administration%20Council%20(SAC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SAC%20has%20often%20resorted%20to%20using%20devastating%20air%20strikes%20and%20scorch%20earth%20tactics%20to%20pummel%20resistance%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition%20forces%20making%20gains%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20tide%20has%20turned%20somewhat%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMyanmar%E2%80%99s%20opposition%20forces%20have%20made%20significant%20inroads%2C%20capturing%20territory%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20northern%20Shan%20state%20in%20a%20three-pronged%20united%20brotherhood%20alliance%2C%20leaving%20the%20junta%20reeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sweeping%20%E2%80%9COperation%201027%E2%80%9D%20offensive%20over%20the%20span%20of%20three%20months%20saw%20dozens%20of%20townships%20and%20hundreds%20of%20junta-held%20military%20bases%20captured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnthony%20Davis%2C%20a%20Myanmar%20security%20expert%2C%20said%20the%20Shan%20state%20offensive%20hit%20the%20junta%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20junta%20has%20neither%20the%20manpower%20reserves%20nor%20organizational%20capacity%20to%20mount%20major%20counter-offensives%20anywhere%20in%20Myanmar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ethnic%20group%20alliance%20captured%20Laukkai%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20the%20Kokang%20Self-Administered%20Zone%2C%20which%20runs%20along%20the%20Myanmar-China%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20China%20because%20of%20the%20potential%20for%20trade%20disruptions%20and%20an%20influx%20of%20refugees%2C%20prompting%20Beijing%20to%20try%20again%20to%20be%20a%20mediator%2C%20where%20twice%20before%20it%20had%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelayed%20elections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%E2%80%99s%20Foreign%20Ministry%20said%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20between%20alliance%20and%20junta%20representatives%20had%20been%20agreed%20with%20all%20parties%20after%20talks%20were%20held%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20only%20days%20later%2C%20reports%20of%20junta%20forces%20firing%20on%20the%20alliance%20saw%20the%20ethnic%20groups%20retaliate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20ceasefire%20in%20Shan%20State%20has%20already%20been%20broken%20by%20both%20sides%20in%20multiple%20locations.%20If%20and%20when%20the%20Brotherhood%20alliance%20decide%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20their%20interest%20to%20go%20back%