%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Built%20Centuries%20Ago%2C%20Akhondji%20Mosque%20and%20Madrasa%20Bulldozed%20in%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03233643%2FMosque-razed.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3EDelhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20morning%20of%20January%2030%2C%20officials%20from%20the%20Delhi%20Development%20Authority%20(DDA)%2C%20accompanied%20by%20police%20personnel%20and%20bulldozers%2C%20conducted%20a%20demolition%20operation%20in%20Mehrauli.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Sanjay%20Van%20area%20witnessed%20the%20demolition%20of%20a%20700-year-old%20mosque%2C%20Masjid%20Akhondji%2C%20an%20adjacent%20madrasa%20and%20a%20small%20temple.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAllegations%20have%20emerged%20that%20the%20DDA%E2%80%99s%20actions%20may%20violate%20high%20court%20orders.%20In%C2%A0%20September%202023%2C%20the%20DDA%20assured%20the%20court%20that%20it%20would%20not%20demolish%20mosques%20and%20properties%20under%20the%20Waqf%20Board%20without%20demarcation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20court%20had%20specifically%20directed%20the%20DDA%20to%20carry%20out%20demarcation%20before%20any%20action%2C%20emphasising%20the%20importance%20of%20determining%20boundaries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20recent%20operation%20bypassed%20the%20demarcation%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Delhi%20high%20court%20on%20Thursday%20(Feburary%201)%20asked%20the%20DDA%20to%20explain%20why%20it%20demolished%20the%20mosque%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArchaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI)%20records%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EScroll.in%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20indicate%20the%20historical%20significance%20of%20the%20Akhondji%20mosque.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPublished%20in%201920%2C%20a%20list%20of%203%2C000%20monuments%20mentions%20the%20mosque%E2%80%99s%20repairs%20around%201853%2C%20although%20its%20construction%20date%20remains%20unknown.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20mosque%20is%20covered%20with%20an%20arched%20roof%20and%20entered%20through%20three%20arches%20supported%20on%20double%20pillars%20of%20grey%20local%20stone.%20It%20is%20built%20of%20rubble%20masonry%20plastered%2C%E2%80%9D%20ASI%20records%20say%20according%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EScroll.in%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20DDA%20razed%20the%20mosque%2C%20the%20madrasa%20and%20the%20adjoining%20graves%2C%20the%20mosque%E2%80%99s%20imam%20Zakir%20Hussain%20and%20his%20family%20have%20been%20left%20without%20a%20shelter%20as%20his%20home%20was%20also%20razed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWatch%20the%20video%20to%20know%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FgfYxEqfFJ2s%3Fsi%3DIXOBfcfzspnUxRAw%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707013855000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03233643%2FMosque-razed.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fakhondji-mosque-madrasa-demolished-delhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20high%20court%20on%20Thursday%20asked%20the%20Delhi%20Development%20Authority%20to%20explain%20why%20it%20demolished%20the%20mosque.%20It%20is%20in%20an%20ASI%20list%20of%203%2C000%20monuments%20published%20in%201920.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fakhondji-mosque-madrasa-demolished-