ernment's%20focus%20on%20four%20categories%20of%20society%20-%20the%20poor%2C%20women%2C%20young%20men%20and%20women%2C%20and%20farmers.%20The%20Modi%20government's%20focus%20on%20women%20and%20women-led%20development%2C%20its%20Nari%20Shakti%20motto%2C%20is%20widely%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20major%20election%20plank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EFDI%2C%20Or%20'First%20Develop%20India'%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20said%20FDI%20(foreign%20direct%20investment)%20inflow%20between%202014%20and%202023%20had%20marked%20a%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20era%26quot%3B.%20The%20sum%20of%20%24596%20billion%20was%20twice%20that%20between%202005%20and%202014%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20encourage%20sustained%20foreign%20investment%2C%20the%20government%20is%20negotiating%20bilateral%20investment%20treaties%20with%20our%20foreign%20partners%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20FDI%2C%20or%20'First%20Develop%20India'%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EGlobal%20Challenges%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Finance%20Minister%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20global%20context%20of%20development%2C%20acknowledging%20that%20increasingly%20fragile%20geopolitical%20situations%20across%20the%20world%20-%20such%20as%20wars%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20Gaza%2C%20and%20tension%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20spectre%20of%20terrorism%20-%20had%20created%20new%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20challenges%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20hailed%20the%20Modi%20government%20for%20delivering%20high%20growth%20and%20ensuring%20it%20maintains%20its%20%26quot%3Bexemplary%20track%20record%20of%20Governance%2C%20Development%2C%20and%20Performance%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BOur%20government%20has%20provided%20transparent%2C%20accountable%2C%20and%20people-centric%2C%20trust-based%20administration%2C%20with%20citizen-first%2C%20minimum-government%2C%20and%20maximum-governance%20mode.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtvprofit.com%2Fwidget%2Fstate-of