ion%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20video%20%5Bon%20YouTube%5D%20where%20I%20found%20someone%20teaching%20how%20to%20connect%20words%20and%20shorten%20them%20in%20spoken%20English%20conversation.%20That%20captivated%20me%20and%20I%20was%20interested%20to%20learn%20that%20kind%20of%20English%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Dhiraj%20left%20Kerala%2C%20he%20began%20learning%20the%20%5BAmerican%5D%20accent%20that%20he%20currently%20employs%20in%20his%20reels%20by%20watching%20a%20plethora%20of%20videos%20online.%20Also%2C%20by%20the%20time%20he%20came%20back%20home%20to%20his%20village%2C%20he%20had%20a%20basic%20Panasonic%20P91%20smartphone%20with%20a%204G%20internet%20connection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20motivation%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20speak%20English%20in%20that%20manner%20came%20from%20a%20desire%20to%20communicate%20faster.%20As%20he%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20used%20to%20speak%20English%20very%20slowly.%20Learning%20how%20to%20speak%20in%20an%20%5BWestern%5D%20accent%20was%20more%20about%20learning%20to%20speak%20the%20language%20faster.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20I%20had%20an%20interest%20in%20singing%20English%20songs%20like%20those%20in%20the%20West%20do.%20If%20I%20wanted%20to%20sing%20in%20their%20accent%2C%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20to%20speak%20in%20their%20accent%20too.%20At%20the%20institute%20in%20Kerala%2C%20I%20developed%20a%20strong%20interest%20in%20learning%20the%20English%20language%2C%20and%20the%20desire%20to%20speak%20it%20faster%20and%20in%20a%20Western%20accent.%20But%20since%20our%20access%20to%20mobile%20phones%20was%20limited%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20learn%20much.%20When%20I%20came%20back%20home%20during%20the%20lockdown%20with%20all%20the%20free%20time%20in%20the%20world%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20started%20learning%20and%20practising%20the%20accent%20you%20hear%20in%20my%20reels%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%